:\"zerif_ourfocus_subtitle\";s:25:\"Great futures start here.\";s:23:\"zerif_bottomribbon_text\";s:33:\"Be part of a change in the World.\";s:30:\"zerif_bottomribbon_buttonlabel\";s:7:\"donate!\";s:19:\"zerif_aboutus_title\";s:8:\"about us\";s:22:\"zerif_aboutus_subtitle\";s:26:\"We are more than a charity\";s:26:\"zerif_aboutus_biglefttitle\";s:56:\"Rebuilding communities for families, one home at a time.\";s:18:\"zerif_aboutus_text\";s:873:\"The Foundation for Social Entrepreneurship Development \'To Be Together\' was established in 2007 by the \'Be Together\' Mutual Aid Association from Cieszyn. The ideas of the Foundation result to a large extent from the Association\'s experience, but the scope of its activity is extended by running a social enterprise, supporting social cooperatives, social enterprises, companies focused on social activities, associations and other forms of social activity based on values ​​of solidarity, reciprocity and cooperation .\n\n\nThe Foundation for the Development of Social Entrepreneurship \"Be Together\" with Cieszyn implements numerous projects aimed at activating the unemployed and those threatened with social exclusion through work and education. By creating new jobs in the social enterprise we run, we support the return to society of people at risk of marginalization.\";s:28:\"zerif_aboutus_feature1_title\";s:11:\"our impact \";s:27:\"zerif_aboutus_feature1_text\";s:30:\"Opening minds, changing lives.\";s:25:\"zerif_aboutus_feature1_nr\";i:88;s:28:\"zerif_aboutus_feature2_title\";s:20:\"passion inside of us\";s:27:\"zerif_aboutus_feature2_text\";s:14:\"Hope in Motion\";s:28:\"zerif_aboutus_feature3_title\";s:12:\"our Services\";s:27:\"zerif_aboutus_feature3_text\";s:30:\"Lifting up with hands of help.\";s:28:\"zerif_aboutus_feature4_title\";s:23:\"Happiness we distrubute\";s:27:\"zerif_aboutus_feature4_text\";s:34:\"A safe place where healing begins.\";s:19:\"zerif_ourteam_title\";s:19:\"our passiniote crew\";s:22:\"zerif_ourteam_subtitle\";s:35:\"Bringing out the best in each other\";s:21:\"zerif_latestnews_show\";b:1;s:22:\"zerif_ribbonright_text\";s:37:\"Empowering youth for a bright future.\";s:29:\"zerif_ribbonright_buttonlabel\";s:27:\"check out our facebook page\";s:11:\"custom_logo\";i:83;s:16:\"background_image\";s:68:\"http://localhost/testsite/wp-content/themes/zerif-lite/images/bg.jpg\";s:21:\"background_position_x\";s:6:\"center\";s:21:\"background_position_y\";s:6:\"center\";s:17:\"background_preset\";s:4:\"fill\";s:15:\"background_size\";s:5:\"cover\";s:17:\"background_repeat\";s:9:\"no-repeat\";s:21:\"background_attachment\";s:5:\"fixed\";}', 'yes'),
