(344, '_transient_feed_29f7869e391c2a2c562f0042f814b9de', 'a:4:{s:5:\"child\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:3:\"rss\";a:1:{i:0;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:3:\"\n\n\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:7:\"version\";s:3:\"2.0\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:7:\"channel\";a:1:{i:0;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:49:\"\n	\n	\n	\n	\n	\n	\n	\n	\n	\n	\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n	\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:3:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:43:\"IsItWP – WordPress Technology Lookup Tool\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:22:\"https://www.isitwp.com\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:13:\"lastBuildDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Fri, 09 Nov 2018 18:58:45 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"language\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:5:\"en-US\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:9:\"generator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:30:\"https://wordpress.org/?v=4.9.8\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"item\";a:10:{i:0;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:39:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:6:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:51:\"LiveChat Review: Is It the Best Live Chat Software?\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:50:\"https://www.isitwp.com/wordpress-plugins/livechat/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:58:\"https://www.isitwp.com/wordpress-plugins/livechat/#respond\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Fri, 09 Nov 2018 18:55:04 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:56:\"https://www.isitwp.com/?post_type=isitwp_plugin&p=224270\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:581:\"<p>Do you want to add live chat to your WordPress site for instant messaging? Putting live chat on your site helps you to communicate better with your site visitors and convert more visitors into leads. To add live chat in WordPress, you can use the popular LiveChat software but is it the best choice? In [&#8230;]</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wordpress-plugins/livechat/\">LiveChat Review: Is It the Best Live Chat Software?</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com\">IsItWP - WordPress Technology Lookup Tool</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:10:\"Sunita Rai\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:20381:\"<p>Do you want to add live chat to your WordPress site for instant messaging? Putting live chat on your site helps you to communicate better with your site visitors and convert more visitors into leads. To add live chat in WordPress, you can use the popular <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/livechat-inc/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">LiveChat</a> software but is it the best choice? </p>\n<p>In this LiveChat review, we’ll check out how it works, its features and functionalities, pricing, and more to help you decide if it’s the right tool for you. </p>\n<h3>About LiveChat Software</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/livechat-inc/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/live-chat.png\" alt=\"LiveChat Inc\" width=\"775\" height=\"350\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-218486\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/live-chat.png 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/live-chat-300x135.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/live-chat-768x347.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/livechat-inc/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">LiveChat</a> is one of the <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-live-chat-software-compared/\">best live chat software plugins</a> available on the market. It’s an application that allows you to add live chat to your website and provide the fastest response to your users. It enables your site visitors to live chat with your team about any support and sales query. </p>\n<p>LiveChat comes with many useful chat tools such as message sneak-peek, file sharing, timeline, delivery status, and notifications. It has more interesting options to engage customers like automatic and personal greetings. There’re also feedback options to rate chat, comments, tickets, etc. </p>\n<p>The LiveChat interface is simple and easy to learn. There’re team management options like agent groups, agent roles, work scheduler, chat supervision etc. to keep your chat support team organized. It also provides reports and analytics including basic statistics, chat reports, ticket reports, daily summary and more. </p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/livechat-inc/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">LiveChat</a> features seamless integration with 130+ tools including CMS platforms like WordPress and Drupal, eCommerce applications like Shopify and BigCommerce, and help desk applications like Knowledge Base and Zendesk. To add LiveChat on your <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/how-to-make-a-website-step-by-step/\">WordPress website</a>, there’s a free plugin in the official WordPress plugin repository. </p>\n<h3>Why You Need to Add Live Chat to Your Site?</h3>\n<p>Live chat is one of the fastest ways to respond visitors on your site. It’s way faster than emails and phones. Adding live chat option on your site enables your users to ask a question as it pops up in their head. And, an instant response from your end makes communication just great!</p>\n<p>Most often, live chat is used for support and sales. If you’re a company selling some products and services, you’ll need live chat for both support and sales. When a customer tackles a problem while using your product, they can instantly contact you via live chat. Then, you can offer an instant help. </p>\n<p>Such enhanced communication will surely enhance your impression in the user’s mind. And, that will definitely pay off in the long run as they share it with word of mouth and other media. For the least, they’ll be your customers until you’re doing the business. </p>\n<p>Live chat is great for <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-lead-generation-plugins-compared/\">lead generation</a> and sales as you can direct a user directly to the checkout page when you know they’re interested in a product. Many users quit the idea of buying a product just because they can’t find a little piece of complementary information. So, you can capture each of such users and convert them into customers. </p>\n<p>In the nutshell, live chat enhances the user experience, engagement, lead generation, and sales. It’s a simple yet great way to grow your business and become successful. </p>\n<h3>LiveChat Review: Getting Started with LiveChat</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/livechat-inc/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">LiveChat</a> is a premium live chat software but they’ve free 30-day trial to start with. So you can sign up free and use the software free for 30 days, explore its features, and decide whether to continue with a subscription or discontinue using it. It’s a great option as you can sign up free with just an email address at first. </p>\n<p>To get started, you’ll need to visit the <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/livechat-inc/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">LiveChat website</a> and click <strong>Sign Up Free</strong> button. </p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/signup-free-livechat.jpg\" alt=\"signup-free-livechat\" width=\"775\" height=\"413\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-224274\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/signup-free-livechat.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/signup-free-livechat-300x160.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/signup-free-livechat-768x409.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></p>\n<p>Now you should enter your <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/how-to-create-a-free-business-email/\">business email</a> to start the LiveChat signup process. Alternatively, you can also sign up with your Google account. </p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/enter-email-livechat-signup.jpg\" alt=\"enter-email-livechat-signup\" width=\"775\" height=\"387\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-224275\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/enter-email-livechat-signup.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/enter-email-livechat-signup-300x150.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/enter-email-livechat-signup-768x384.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></p>\n<p>Then in the second step, you’ll need to enter your website address. Then, also choose chat purpose. </p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/enter-site-address-livechat-signup.jpg\" alt=\"enter-site-address-livechat-signup\" width=\"775\" height=\"413\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-224276\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/enter-site-address-livechat-signup.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/enter-site-address-livechat-signup-300x160.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/enter-site-address-livechat-signup-768x409.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></p>\n<p>In the third and last step, you can choose an industry type, number of employees, and audience type. If you’re planning to live chat only with your customers, you can check <strong>B2C</strong> only. But if you want to chat with other businesses as well, also check <strong>B2B</strong>. And, <strong>Internal Use</strong> if you want it for communication for internal use. </p>\n<p>Then click <strong>Create Account</strong> button. </p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/create-account-livechat.jpg\" alt=\"create-account-livechat\" width=\"775\" height=\"499\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-224277\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/create-account-livechat.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/create-account-livechat-300x193.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/create-account-livechat-768x494.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></p>\n<p>Now, you’ll see a sign in page. Sign in with your email and password that you used in step 1. And, the signup process is complete. </p>\n<p>Then, you’ll see the next steps of LiveChat setup process. In the next step, you’ll need to install LiveChat code on your site. </p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/install-code-livechat.jpg\" alt=\"install-code-livechat\" width=\"775\" height=\"630\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-224278\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/install-code-livechat.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/install-code-livechat-300x244.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/install-code-livechat-768x624.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></p>\n<p>For a WordPress site, it’s easy and safe with the LiveChat plugin. We’ll show you steps to installing LiveChat plugin and connecting LiveChat with WordPress in the next section below. So, you can click <strong>I’ll do it later</strong> to skip to next step. </p>\n<p>In step 3, you can choose a chat theme. </p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/chat-theme-livechat.jpg\" alt=\"chat-theme-livechat\" width=\"775\" height=\"493\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-224279\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/chat-theme-livechat.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/chat-theme-livechat-300x191.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/chat-theme-livechat-768x489.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></p>\n<p>Step 4 lets you personalize your LiveChat profile. You can upload a profile photo and set a welcome message. </p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/personalize-livechat.jpg\" alt=\"personalize-livechat\" width=\"775\" height=\"493\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-224280\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/personalize-livechat.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/personalize-livechat-300x191.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/personalize-livechat-768x489.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></p>\n<p>Then finally in step 5, you can add agents to your team.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/create-agents-livechat.jpg\" alt=\"create-agents-livechat\" width=\"775\" height=\"493\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-224281\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/create-agents-livechat.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/create-agents-livechat-300x191.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/create-agents-livechat-768x489.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></p>\n<p>After adding the total number of agents, you can click <strong>Go to Application</strong> button. </p>\n<p>Now, you’ll see LiveChat interface open. There you’ll see a notification at the top that you haven’t installed LiveChat on your site. Now, we’ll show you how to install it on your site. </p>\n<h3>Installing LiveChat on Your WordPress Site</h3>\n<p>Once you’ve completed LiveChat setup process, you’re now ready to install it on your WordPress site. It’s a simple process of connecting your LiveChat account with your WordPress site. There’s a free LiveChat plugin for WordPress for this purpose.  </p>\n<p>To start with, login to your WordPress dashboard and visit <strong>Plugins &raquo; Add New</strong>. Type <strong>LiveChat</strong> in the search box first. Once it appears, install and activate it.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/install-livechat-plugin.jpg\" alt=\"install-livechat-plugin\" width=\"775\" height=\"426\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-224282\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/install-livechat-plugin.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/install-livechat-plugin-300x165.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/install-livechat-plugin-768x422.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></p>\n<p>After it’s activated, you can see <strong>LiveChat</strong> menu added to your dashboard panel. Go to <strong>LiveChat &raquo; Settings</strong>. </p>\n<p>Next, you’ll need to click <strong>Sign in with LiveChat</strong> button to connect LiveChat with WordPress. </p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/connect-livechat-with-wordpress.jpg\" alt=\"connect-livechat-with-wordpress\" width=\"775\" height=\"411\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-224283\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/connect-livechat-with-wordpress.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/connect-livechat-with-wordpress-300x159.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/connect-livechat-with-wordpress-768x407.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></p>\n<p>After that, you’ll see your WordPress site connected with LiveChat. </p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/livechat-installed-in-wordpress.jpg\" alt=\"livechat-installed-in-wordpress\" width=\"775\" height=\"343\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-224284\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/livechat-installed-in-wordpress.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/livechat-installed-in-wordpress-300x133.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/livechat-installed-in-wordpress-768x340.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></p>\n<p>Click on the <strong>Open web application</strong> to go to the LiveChat interface. </p>\n<p>Now you can manage your chats, chat team, and everything from there. </p>\n<p>If you check your website, you’ll see LiveChat screen added to your site.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/livechat-added-on-wordpress.jpg\" alt=\"livechat-added-on-wordpress\" width=\"385\" height=\"558\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-224291\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/livechat-added-on-wordpress.jpg 385w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/livechat-added-on-wordpress-207x300.jpg 207w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 385px) 100vw, 385px\" /></p>\n<h3>Checking out LiveChat Features</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/livechat-inc/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">LiveChat</a> is a feature-rich application for adding live chat to your site. It has plenty of chat tools, customization options, and team management features. </p>\n<p><strong>1. Simple yet complete chat screen</strong></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/livechat-chat-screen.jpg\" alt=\"livechat-chat-screen\" width=\"775\" height=\"478\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-224285\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/livechat-chat-screen.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/livechat-chat-screen-300x185.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/livechat-chat-screen-768x474.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></p>\n<p>You can see the list of chats, chat box, and customer’s contact info at the same screen. It makes it easy to manage all chats at once based on the priority. </p>\n<p><strong>2. Comprehensive Chat Reports</strong></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/livechat-reports.jpg\" alt=\"livechat-reports\" width=\"775\" height=\"489\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-224286\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/livechat-reports.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/livechat-reports-300x189.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/livechat-reports-768x485.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/livechat-inc/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">LiveChat</a> provides highly comprehensive reports where you can see stats for chats, tickets, and eCommerce. </p>\n<p><strong>Full Customization Made Possible</strong> </p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/livechat-settings.jpg\" alt=\"livechat-settings\" width=\"775\" height=\"489\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-224287\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/livechat-settings.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/livechat-settings-300x189.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/livechat-settings-768x485.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/livechat-inc/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">LiveChat</a> allows you to fully customize how your chat interface looks like and how it works. You can customize anything by going to the <strong>Settings</strong> menu in your LiveChat account.</p>\n<h3>LiveChat Software: Pricing and Support</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/livechat-inc/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">LiveChat</a> is a premium live chat software however you can always start with their 30-days free trial. </p>\n<p>If you’re satisfied with its features after 30 days, you can subscribe to one of their plans. There’re 4 pricing plans available. </p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/livechat-inc/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/livechat-pricing.jpg\" alt=\"livechat-pricing\" width=\"775\" height=\"518\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-224288\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/livechat-pricing.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/livechat-pricing-300x201.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/livechat-pricing-768x513.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>The basic LiveChat plan is <strong>Starter</strong>. It’s suitable for small office or home office needs. You can create unlimited agent accounts but it allows only 60-day chat history and basic chat customization. If you need unlimited chat history and full chat customization, you’ll need to buy <strong>team</strong> plan at least. </p>\n<p>The Starter costs $16 monthly per logged in agent. </p>\n<p>Second, <strong>Team</strong> plan is for a full-time support team. It allows you to create unlimited agent accounts, see unlimited chat history, full chat customization, and basic reporting. It costs $33 monthly per logged in agent. </p>\n<p>Third, <strong>Business</strong> plan is the most popular plan. It’s suitable for bigger firms to organize customer service department. It has more additional advanced features than the Team plan like work scheduler, staffing prediction, etc. It costs $50 monthly per logged in agent. </p>\n<p>The highest priced LiveChat plan is called <strong>Enterprise</strong>. It has the most advanced features. It’s designed for Fortune 500 companies or alike. It costs $149 monthly per logged in agent. </p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/livechat-inc/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">LiveChat</a> provides 24/4 dedicated support via live chat. Plus, it has a rich knowledgebase with tutorials, webinars, etc. to help you with any problem you tackle while using this software. </p>\n<h3>Our Verdict on Using LiveChat Software on Your WordPress Site</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/livechat-inc/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">LiveChat</a> is undoubtedly a great chat tool suitable for all level users. It’s useful for small businesses as well as big Fortune 500 companies. </p>\n<p>Using LiveChat is easy. It has simple user interface, yet powerful features to run live chat on your website efficiently. Installing LiveChat on WordPress is easy with their free plugin as you don’t need to touch a single piece of code to install and use. </p>\n<p>We believe that <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/livechat-inc/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">LiveChat</a> is the perfect live chat software for adding live chat to your WordPress site. It has a complete set of features you’ll ever need to run live chat. Its integration with eCommerce and other tools makes your life just easy. </p>\n<p>We give it 4.5 out of 5 stars. Here’s the breakdown of our review score: </p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wordpress-plugins/livechat/\">LiveChat Review: Is It the Best Live Chat Software?</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com\">IsItWP - WordPress Technology Lookup Tool</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:55:\"https://www.isitwp.com/wordpress-plugins/livechat/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:1;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:51:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:54:\"24 Best WordPress Education Themes (Compared) – 2018\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:55:\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-education-themes/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:63:\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-education-themes/#respond\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Thu, 08 Nov 2018 10:01:23 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:4:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:9:\"Resources\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:21:\"best wordpress themes\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:2;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:16:\"education themes\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:3;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:14:\"premium themes\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:32:\"https://www.isitwp.com/?p=223651\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:646:\"<p>Are you looking for the best education themes for WordPress? Whether you’re in charge of a school’s website or selling your own courses out of your home, you’ll need the perfect theme to captivate your students. The right theme can help convert visitors into students, showcase your courses, enhance your professional credibility, and skyrocket your [&#8230;]</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-education-themes/\">24 Best WordPress Education Themes (Compared) &#8211; 2018</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com\">IsItWP - WordPress Technology Lookup Tool</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:14:\"Editorial Team\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:30621:\"<p>Are you looking for the best education themes for WordPress? Whether you’re in charge of a school’s website or selling your own courses out of your home, you’ll need the perfect theme to captivate your students. The right theme can help convert visitors into students, showcase your courses, enhance your professional credibility, and skyrocket your online success.</p>\n<p>In this article, we’ll share the 24 best WordPress education themes on the market. They’re all responsive, so any theme you choose from this list will look fantastic on any device.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/teslathemes-motive/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">1. Motive</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/teslathemes-motive/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Motive.jpg\" alt=\"Motive\" width=\"775\" height=\"230\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-223747\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Motive.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Motive-300x89.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Motive-768x228.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Packed with easy-to-use shortcodes, the Motive theme is eye-catching and modern. Using grid, masonry, or mosaic layouts, you can showcase your educational portfolio effortlessly.</p>\n<p>Powered by the ever-popular Tesla Framework, Motive features parallax backgrounds, custom post types, featured images, featured videos, custom widgets, its own form builder, and more.</p>\n<p>It’s highly customizable and you can tweak it endlessly until you get it looking exactly how you want it. Or, if you’re in a rush, you can import one of their pre-built demo sites and simply change the content to your own.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/teslathemes-motive/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get Started with Motive Today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/wpzoom-academia-pro/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">2. Academia Pro</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/wpzoom-academia-pro/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/academia-pro.png\" alt=\"academia pro\" width=\"550\" height=\"274\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-223748\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/academia-pro.png 550w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/academia-pro-300x149.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Flexibility is the name of the game with Academia Pro. You can use a 3 column layout or a 2 column layout. And you can put your sidebar on either the left or right side. Plus, you can change the layout of each page individually; meaning, you can have a 3 column layout on one page and a 2 column layout on another!</p>\n<p>The header comes with 3 menu options. You can use all of them or none of them. Personally, we like the menu option that comes with an eye-catching call-to-action button!</p>\n<p>You can also use your own, custom logo for your header image. Academia Pro is perfect for schools, or home educators who’ve developed their own brand.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/wpzoom-academia-pro/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get Started with Academia Pro Today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/mojomarketplace-elms/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">3. Elms</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/mojomarketplace-elms/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/elms.jpg\" alt=\"elms\" width=\"773\" height=\"324\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-223749\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/elms.jpg 773w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/elms-300x126.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/elms-768x322.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 773px) 100vw, 773px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Elms is one of the best WordPress education themes because it includes its own unique <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-lms-plugins-compared/\" title=\"7 Best WordPress LMS Plugins Compared\">Learning Management System</a> (LMS). You can create free and paid courses, create quizzes, and manage your teachers and students with ease.</p>\n<p>The base elements of the theme include 30 header designs, 8 layout designs, unlimited customizable colors, Google fonts, and endless widgets.</p>\n<p>Elms comes with its own drag and drop builder so you can create your own layouts without having to touch any code. Choose from an assortment of columns, rows, and effects when editing your site’s pages.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/mojomarketplace-elms/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get Started with Elms Today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/mojomarketplace-educate/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">4. Educate</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/mojomarketplace-educate/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/educate.jpg\" alt=\"educate\" width=\"775\" height=\"323\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-223750\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/educate.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/educate-300x125.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/educate-768x320.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Educate comes bundled with <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wordpress-plugins/visual-composer/\" title=\"WPBakery Page Builder Review (Formerly Visual Composer)\">WPBakery</a> (formerly Visual Composer) for free, allowing you to utilize its powerful drag and drop builder.</p>\n<p>It includes an advanced admin panel for educators. It’s also highly customizable, featuring over 500 different header styles, multiple layout options, AJAX search capabilities, custom widgets, and unlimited font and icon options.</p>\n<p>Educate also comes bundled with Revolution Slider for free, which gives you the power to create tantalizing image slideshows on your homepage to attract new students.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/mojomarketplace-educate/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get Started with Educate Today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/mojomarketplace-edukado/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">5. Edukado</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/mojomarketplace-edukado/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/edukado.jpg\" alt=\"edukado\" width=\"774\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-223751\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/edukado.jpg 774w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/edukado-300x132.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/edukado-768x337.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 774px) 100vw, 774px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Featuring its own drag and drop page builder, Educado is a perfect theme for educational institutes looking to <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/how-to-make-a-website-step-by-step/\">get their website online</a> quickly.</p>\n<p>Educado is compatible with WooCommerce and most LMS plugins, allowing you to earn money from online courses and educational products.</p>\n<p>With over a dozen pre-built layouts designed specifically for education-based websites, Educado will get you up and running in no time flat.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/mojomarketplace-edukado/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get Started with Educado!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/artisanthemes-nayma/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">6. Nayma</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/artisanthemes-nayma/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/nayma-1.jpg\" alt=\"nayma\" width=\"775\" height=\"296\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-223752\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/nayma-1.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/nayma-1-300x115.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/nayma-1-768x293.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Thanks to its 1-click demo installer and 8 ready-made websites, Nayma lets you build your website in a matter of minutes. It also includes its own easy-to-use <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-page-builders-compared/\" title=\"7 Best Drag and Drop WordPress Page Builders Compared\">drag and drop builder</a> if you prefer to <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/how-to-make-a-website-step-by-step/\" title=\"How to Make a Website in 2018- Step by Step\">build your website from scratch</a>, zero coding skills required.</p>\n<p>It features modules for image sliders, pricing tables, testimonials, and more. It’s also WooCommerce ready.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/artisanthemes-nayma/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get Started with Nayma Today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/arraythemes-paperback/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">7. Paperback</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/arraythemes-paperback/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/paperback.jpg\" alt=\"paperback\" width=\"775\" height=\"356\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-223753\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/paperback.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/paperback-300x138.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/paperback-768x353.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>If you’re looking for a magazine-style theme that lets you showcase image galleries, videos, and audio clips, then Paperback is the perfect choice.</p>\n<p>Paperback lets you choose from several built-in color schemes which you can customize to suit your brand.</p>\n<p>You can choose a 1, 2, or 3 column layout. Infinite scroll is also available. And your content will always be found when it’s needed thanks to the AJAX search functionality.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/arraythemes-paperback/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get Started with Paperback Today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/mojomarketplace-wp-education/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">8. WP Education</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/mojomarketplace-wp-education/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/WP-Education.png\" alt=\"WP Education\" width=\"772\" height=\"339\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-223754\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/WP-Education.png 772w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/WP-Education-300x132.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/WP-Education-768x337.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 772px) 100vw, 772px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Powered by LearnPress, WP Education isn’t just a theme: it’s a powerful Learning Management System. You can create and sell courses, design quizzes, and manage your students easily.</p>\n<p>WP Education comes with support for The Events Calendar, for booking purposes; and WooCommerce, to turn your site into a full-fledged income generating machine.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/mojomarketplace-wp-education/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get Started with WP Education Today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/themes/edumag/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">9. EduMag</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/themes/edumag/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Edumag.jpg\" alt=\"Edumag\" width=\"774\" height=\"364\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-223755\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Edumag.jpg 774w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Edumag-300x141.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Edumag-768x361.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 774px) 100vw, 774px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Easily customizable and featuring a live preview option, EduMag is a magazine-style theme created specifically for educators.</p>\n<p>It posts a handy social media widget, is WooCommerce compatible, and is translation-ready.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/themes/edumag/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get Started with EduMag Today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/themes/kindergarten-education/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">10. Kindergarten Education</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/themes/kindergarten-education/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/kindergarten-education.png\" alt=\"kindergarten education\" width=\"775\" height=\"265\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-223756\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/kindergarten-education.png 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/kindergarten-education-300x103.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/kindergarten-education-768x263.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Our list of the best education themes for WordPress wouldn’t be complete without Kindergarten Education. While most of the themes featured here focus on adult learning, Kindergarten Education was made specifically with a younger crowd in mind. Create a minimal-yet-fun website aimed at younger pupils.</p>\n<p>The theme itself is <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-seo-tools-to-grow-your-site-traffic/\">SEO-friendly</a>, translation-ready, and boasts an attractive banner with a large call-to-action button to entice clicks and conversions.</p>\n<p>Kindergarten Education runs on the Bootstrap framework, and is highly optimized for speed. You can also sell products thanks to its WooCommerce integration.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/themes/kindergarten-education/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get Started with Kindergarten Education Today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/themes/edu-care/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">11. Edu Care</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/themes/edu-care/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/edu-care.png\" alt=\"edu care\" width=\"775\" height=\"274\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-223757\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/edu-care.png 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/edu-care-300x106.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/edu-care-768x272.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Attractive, modern, and easy-to-use, Edu Care is perfect for universities, colleges, and any other type of school’s website.</p>\n<p>Edu Care is translation-ready, making it a perfect choice for educational institutes looking to attract students with diverse language backgrounds.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/themes/edu-care/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get Started with Edu Care Today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/themes/education-consultr/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">12. Education Consultr</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/themes/education-consultr/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Education-Consultr.png\" alt=\"Education Consultr\" width=\"775\" height=\"282\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-223758\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Education-Consultr.png 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Education-Consultr-300x109.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Education-Consultr-768x279.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>A child theme of the popular Business Consultr, Education Consultr is an elegant, blue-colored theme designed specifically for educators.</p>\n<p>You can customize your theme’s header, logo area, and menus. It features a professional-looking 2-column layout, several post formats, featured images, and is translation ready.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/themes/education-consultr/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get Started with Education Consultr Today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/themes/enlighten/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">13. Enlighten</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/themes/enlighten/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/enlighten.png\" alt=\"enlighten\" width=\"775\" height=\"299\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-223759\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/enlighten.png 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/enlighten-300x116.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/enlighten-768x296.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Available completely for free, Enlighten is one of the best WordPress education themes for colleges, universities, and anyone else promoting higher learning.</p>\n<p>Customizable via a live preview, Enlighten is extremely flexible. It features homepage sliders, multiple education-specific page sections, an image carousel, and multiple widget areas.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/themes/enlighten/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get Started with Enlighten Today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/themify-ultra/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">14. Ultra</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/themify-ultra/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Ultra-1.png\" alt=\"Ultra\" width=\"775\" height=\"272\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-223760\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Ultra-1.png 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Ultra-1-300x105.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Ultra-1-768x270.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Ultra is one of our <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/top-wordpress-themes/\">favorite WordPress themes</a> of all time, so it’s no surprise it made our list of the best education themes for WordPress.</p>\n<p>Created by Themify, Ultra comes with over 60 pre-designed layouts; many of which work well for educators and schools. It also has an intuitive drag and drop builder included so you can customize your site with ease.</p>\n<p>Want more information? Read our full <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wordpress-themes/themify-ultra/\" title=\"Themify Ultra\">review of the Ultra theme</a>.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/themify-ultra/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get Started with Ultra Today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/wpzoom-presence/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">15. Presence</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/wpzoom-presence/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/presence.png\" alt=\"presence\" width=\"775\" height=\"306\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-223761\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/presence.png 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/presence-300x118.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/presence-768x303.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Presence is flexible, and perfect for educational websites featuring a blog or an online shop.</p>\n<p>Import any of the dozens of pre-built layouts, or utilize the intuitive drag and drop builder, and get your site started immediately.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/wpzoom-presence/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get Started with Presence Today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/arraythemes-lenscap/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">16. Lenscap</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/arraythemes-lenscap/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/lenscap-hero-1.jpg\" alt=\"lenscap\" width=\"772\" height=\"317\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-223762\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/lenscap-hero-1.jpg 772w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/lenscap-hero-1-300x123.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/lenscap-hero-1-768x315.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 772px) 100vw, 772px\" /></a></p>\n<p>With a sophisticated layout and beautiful typography, Lenscap is amazing for educators looking to showcase their services via photos and videos. We’re in love with the customizable content carousel!</p>\n<p>It also includes multiple color schemes, making it simple to match your site with your brand.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/arraythemes-lenscap/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get Started with Lenscap Today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/cyberchimps-edupro/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">17. Edu Pro</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/cyberchimps-edupro/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/edupro.jpg\" alt=\"edupro\" width=\"772\" height=\"327\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-223764\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/edupro.jpg 772w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/edupro-300x127.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/edupro-768x325.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 772px) 100vw, 772px\" /></a></p>\n<p>The welcome image, with an eye-catching call-to-action button, is the crown jewel of this theme. Edu Pro was designed to increase your conversions and help you generate traffic to your most valued landing pages.</p>\n<p>Effortlessly showcase seminars, courses, training videos, and services with its pre-built layouts. You can also get visitors to sign up to your newsletter thanks to its integration with many of the most popular <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-email-marketing-services-compared/\" title=\"9 Best Email Marketing Services Compared\">email marketing services</a>.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/cyberchimps-edupro/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get Started with Edu Pro Today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/studiopress-monochrome/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">18. Monochrome</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/studiopress-monochrome/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/monochrome-pro.jpg\" alt=\"monochrome\" width=\"775\" height=\"331\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-223765\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/monochrome-pro.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/monochrome-pro-300x128.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/monochrome-pro-768x328.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Simple-yet-substantial, Monochrome was designed by the fine folks at StudioPress and utilizes their famous Genesis framework.</p>\n<p>Making great use of white space, Monochrome is a master of minimal. Your educational website will look distinct, confident, and utterly professional.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/studiopress-monochrome/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get Started with Monochrome Today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/cssigniter-neuton/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">19. Neuton</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/cssigniter-neuton/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/neuton.jpg\" alt=\"neuton\" width=\"775\" height=\"385\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-223766\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/neuton.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/neuton-300x149.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/neuton-768x382.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>A magazine-style layout that stands out from the crowd with its trending topics feature, Neuton is perfect if you’re looking for something truly unique.</p>\n<p>Highly customizable, Neuton features a variety of custom widgets and multiple color schemes. You can even assign a different color scheme for each page you create!</p>\n<p>Don’t feel like customizing your site from scratch? No problem. Neuton includes a 1-click demo installer so you can get started immediately.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/cssigniter-neuton/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get Started with Neuton Today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/studiopress-education-pro/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">20. Education Pro</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/studiopress-education-pro/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/education-pro.jpg\" alt=\"education pro\" width=\"775\" height=\"367\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-223767\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/education-pro.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/education-pro-300x142.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/education-pro-768x364.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Education Pro is for institutions who have a great deal of content to share. This theme is perfect for showcasing text, video, and audio posts.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/studiopress-education-pro/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get Started with Education Pro Today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/education-wp/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">21. Education WP</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/education-wp/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/education-wp.png\" alt=\"education wp\" width=\"772\" height=\"361\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-223768\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/education-wp.png 772w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/education-wp-300x140.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/education-wp-768x359.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 772px) 100vw, 772px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Complete with its own LMS, Education WP is quick to set up thanks to over 14 pre-built demo sites you can install. Or, if you feel like building your site from scratch, you can use WPBakery or SiteOrigin’s drag and drop builders.</p>\n<p>Designed to be a multilingual site, this theme is WooCommerce ready and performance optimized.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/education-wp/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get Started with Education WP Today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/eikra-education/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">22. Eikra Education</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/eikra-education/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Eikra-Education.png\" alt=\"Eikra Education\" width=\"774\" height=\"306\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-223769\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Eikra-Education.png 774w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Eikra-Education-300x119.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Eikra-Education-768x304.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 774px) 100vw, 774px\" /></a></p>\n<p>This contemporary theme is great for a variety of education centers. It comes with the LearnPress LMS plugin, so you’ll have all the features you need to create powerful online courses.</p>\n<p>You can get started quickly with Eikra Education thanks to its 1-click demo import. Or, you can build your site from scratch using WPBakery, the included drag and drop builder.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/eikra-education/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get Started with Eikra Education Today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/edugate-education/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">23. Edugate Education</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/edugate-education/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/edugate.png\" alt=\"edugate\" width=\"774\" height=\"335\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-223770\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/edugate.png 774w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/edugate-300x130.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/edugate-768x332.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 774px) 100vw, 774px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Edugate Education recommends using its theme for schools, libraries, and training centers. It’s also perfect for home educators and private tutors.</p>\n<p>It’s a modern theme with a creative flair, perfect for enticing new students.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/edugate-education/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get Started with Edugate Education Today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/education-pack/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">24. Education Pack</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/education-pack/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/education-pack.png\" alt=\"education pack\" width=\"775\" height=\"341\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-223771\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/education-pack.png 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/education-pack-300x132.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/education-pack-768x338.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>As you might expect from the name, Education Pack comes with a “pack” of education site demos that you can easily install to get your website up-and-running. These demos include sites for driving schools, dance academies, design schools, and more!</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/education-pack/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get Started with Education Pack Today!</a></p>\n<p>We hope this article helped you discover the best WordPress Education themes.</p>\n<p>If you found this post useful, you might also enjoy our article on the <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-lms-plugins-compared/\" title=\"7 Best WordPress LMS Plugins Compared (2018)\">best Learning Management System plugins</a>.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-education-themes/\">24 Best WordPress Education Themes (Compared) &#8211; 2018</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com\">IsItWP - WordPress Technology Lookup Tool</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:60:\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-education-themes/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:2;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:51:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:55:\"8 Best WordPress Review Plugins to Boost Online Revenue\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:53:\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-review-plugins/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:61:\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-review-plugins/#respond\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Wed, 07 Nov 2018 10:55:13 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:4:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:17:\"WordPress Plugins\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:14:\"review plugins\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:2;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:14:\"review website\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:3;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:17:\"wordpress plugins\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:32:\"https://www.isitwp.com/?p=223077\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:633:\"<p>Are you looking for the best product review plugins for WordPress? That’s a great idea! If you’re running a review website, you’ll need the perfect plugin to assist you at adding ratings, linking affiliates, displaying snippets, and making your posts overall engaging for your visitors. In this article, we’re going to introduce you to the [&#8230;]</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-review-plugins/\">8 Best WordPress Review Plugins to Boost Online Revenue</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com\">IsItWP - WordPress Technology Lookup Tool</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:14:\"Editorial Team\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:12810:\"<p>Are you looking for the best product review plugins for WordPress? That’s a great idea! If you’re running a review website, you’ll need the perfect plugin to assist you at adding ratings, linking affiliates, displaying snippets, and making your posts overall engaging for your visitors.</p>\n<p>In this article, we’re going to introduce you to the best product review plugins.</p>\n<h3>Why Use a Product Review Plugin?</h3>\n<p>There’s a certain amount of razzle-dazzle readers expect from reviews. They want stars, snippets, links, and fancy-looking comparison tables.</p>\n<p>Sadly, you can’t deliver any of that using the WordPress post editor on its own. Your content might be awesome, but it’ll be missing the “wow” factor your readers expect from a professional review.</p>\n<p>The good news is, by using the best WordPress review plugins, you can give your audience exactly what they crave. Best of all? It’ll be easy for you, as a reviewer.</p>\n<p>The right plugin makes ramping up your reviews to professional-quality effortless. Simply write your review, figure out your scores, and add them to the appropriate sections within the plugin’s editor component.</p>\n<p>To make choosing the correct plugin easy for you, we’ve put together a list of the best WordPress review plugins. Check it out below.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/themeisle-wp-product-review/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">1. WP Product Review</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/themeisle-wp-product-review/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/WP-Product-Review-Plugin.png\" alt=\"WP Product Review Plugin\" width=\"775\" height=\"268\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-223097\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/WP-Product-Review-Plugin.png 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/WP-Product-Review-Plugin-300x104.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/WP-Product-Review-Plugin-768x266.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>If you’re adding multiple reviews to the same page, you’ll love WP Product Review’s shortcodes feature. You can position your shortcodes to add review boxes anywhere within posts and pages.</p>\n<p>Review tables are completely customizable as well. Change the borders, the width, the colors, and the rating icons to perfectly match your brand. There are over 10 different rating icons to choose from, including stars and hearts, so you can really have fun with it.</p>\n<p>In-depth comparison charts are also available. As well as the ability to import product information directly from Amazon.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/themeisle-wp-product-review/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get Started with WP Product Review Today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/mythemeshop-wp-review/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">2. WP Review Pro</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/mythemeshop-wp-review/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/WP-Review-Pro.png\" alt=\"WP Review Pro\" width=\"775\" height=\"323\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-223096\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/WP-Review-Pro.png 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/WP-Review-Pro-300x125.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/WP-Review-Pro-768x320.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>With 16 pre-made, completely customizable, templates, WP Review Pro makes posting reviews a breeze.</p>\n<p>Choose your preferred snippets, your desired rating system, and even showcase readers’ opinions with this versatile plugin. It works perfectly with nearly every theme available.</p>\n<p>WP Review Pro also features near-endless integrations. Integrate your plugin with Google Reviews, Yelp, and Facebook Reviews. You can also integrate it with WooCommerce if you’re <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/how-to-create-an-online-store-step-by-step/\">running an eCommerce website</a>.</p>\n<p>This plugin is mobile-friendly, optimized for speed, translation-ready, and features tons of custom widgets.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/mythemeshop-wp-review/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get Started with WP Review Pro Today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/taqyeem/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">3. Taqyeem</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/taqyeem/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Taqyeem.png\" alt=\"Taqyeem\" width=\"775\" height=\"388\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-223093\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Taqyeem.png 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Taqyeem-300x150.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Taqyeem-768x384.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Taqyeem works with pages, posts, and even custom post types. It’s incredibly easy to use and has tons of customization options to keep your branding on point.</p>\n<p>This plugin is ready to translate, and <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-seo-tools-to-grow-your-site-traffic/\">search engine optimized</a>. There’s even RTL support.</p>\n<p>Choose from unlimited colors, over 500 fonts, and multiple review scoring icons.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/taqyeem/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get Started with Taqyeem Today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/reviewer/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">4. Reviewer</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/reviewer/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Reviewer-WordPress-Plugin.png\" alt=\"Reviewer WordPress Plugin\" width=\"775\" height=\"367\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-223092\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Reviewer-WordPress-Plugin.png 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Reviewer-WordPress-Plugin-300x142.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Reviewer-WordPress-Plugin-768x364.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Add comparison tables and reviews to pages, posts, and custom post types quickly and easily with the Reviewer plugin.</p>\n<p>Just create a template you like and start reviewing. Want users to add reviews too? No problem. Visitors can utilize the template or boxes you’ve created and add their own thoughts to your website. Image uploads are an option for guest reviewers as well.</p>\n<p>Every template you create is mobile-friendly and responsive to adapt to any device.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/reviewer/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get Started with Reviewer Today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/yelp-reviews-pro/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">5. Yelp Reviews Pro</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/yelp-reviews-pro/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Yelp-Reviews-Pro.png\" alt=\"Yelp Reviews Pro\" width=\"775\" height=\"392\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-223091\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Yelp-Reviews-Pro.png 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Yelp-Reviews-Pro-300x152.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Yelp-Reviews-Pro-768x388.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Created by Ninja Team, the force behind Ninja Forms, Yelp Reviews Pro integrates with Yelp to show your reviews, profile, and listings. It’s extremely simple to use, and utilizes shortcodes to add needed information to your posts, pages, and widgets.</p>\n<p>If you’re primarily a Yelp reviewer who wants to expand with your own website, this is the plugin for you.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/yelp-reviews-pro/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get Started with Yelp Reviews Pro Today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/all-in-one-schemaorg-rich-snippets/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">6. All in One Schema Rich Snippets</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/all-in-one-schemaorg-rich-snippets/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Schema-Rich-Snippets.png\" alt=\"Schema Rich Snippets\" width=\"775\" height=\"226\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-223090\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Schema-Rich-Snippets.png 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Schema-Rich-Snippets-300x87.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Schema-Rich-Snippets-768x224.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>If you’re looking to stand out from the crowd on search engines, All in One Schema Rich Snippets is the perfect plugin.</p>\n<p>Snippets allow you to condense your reviews into just the most important information. Add summaries of your thoughts, along with photos and ratings, to let search engines know exactly what they should display. Works great with Facebook too!</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/all-in-one-schemaorg-rich-snippets/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get Started with All in One Schema Rich Snippets Today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/rich-reviews/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">7. Rich Reviews</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/rich-reviews/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Rich-Reviews.png\" alt=\"Rich Reviews\" width=\"775\" height=\"279\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-223089\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Rich-Reviews.png 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Rich-Reviews-300x108.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Rich-Reviews-768x276.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>With moderated user submissions, Rich Reviews puts you in complete control of the content posted on your website. It’s one of the best review plugins for WordPress because it utilizes rich snippets, giving you an edge over your search engine competition.</p>\n<p>Add reviews to posts, pages, and any widget-ready area on your website, including sidebars and footers.</p>\n<p>Translation-ready and highly customizable, Rich Reviews is a simple plugin that goes a long way toward <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/how-to-create-a-review-website/\">making your review website</a> great.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/rich-reviews/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get Started with Rich Reviews Today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/wp-customer-reviews/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">8. WP Customer Reviews</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/wp-customer-reviews/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/WP-Customer-Reviews.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"775\" height=\"355\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-223086\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/WP-Customer-Reviews.png 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/WP-Customer-Reviews-300x137.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/WP-Customer-Reviews-768x352.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>WP Customer Reviews is perfect if you’re using a multisite, or multiuser, reviewing platform. It puts you in complete control of user submissions, allowing you to moderate and choose what gets published.</p>\n<p>Reviews are displayed to your readers in an eye-catching way; however, search engines will view the Schema.org microformat. It’s the best of both worlds. Please your audience and the search engine crawlers at the same time!</p>\n<p>Lightweight and speed-optimized, WP Customer Reviews won’t slow down your website; even if you use their custom rating scales and icons.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/wp-customer-reviews/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get Started with WP Customer Reviews Today!</a></p>\n<p>We hope this article helped you discover the best WordPress review plugins.</p>\n<p>If you liked this article, you might enjoy our post on <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/create-a-survey-in-wordpress/\" title=\"How to Easily Create a Survey in WordPress (Step by Step)\">how to easily create a survey in WordPress</a>.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-review-plugins/\">8 Best WordPress Review Plugins to Boost Online Revenue</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com\">IsItWP - WordPress Technology Lookup Tool</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:58:\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-review-plugins/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:3;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:51:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:55:\"11 Best WordPress Quiz Plugins to Boost User Engagement\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:51:\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-quiz-plugins/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:59:\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-quiz-plugins/#respond\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Tue, 06 Nov 2018 10:22:37 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:4:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:17:\"WordPress Plugins\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:12:\"poll plugins\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:2;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:11:\"quiz plugin\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:3;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:13:\"survey plugin\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:32:\"https://www.isitwp.com/?p=222986\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:590:\"<p>Are you looking for the best WordPress quiz plugins? Great idea! Quizzes are a great way to drive traffic to your website and increase user engagement. In this article, we’ll introduce you to the 11 best WordPress quiz plugins on the market. Why Use a Quiz Plugin? Quizzes can be a fun and effective part [&#8230;]</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-quiz-plugins/\">11 Best WordPress Quiz Plugins to Boost User Engagement</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com\">IsItWP - WordPress Technology Lookup Tool</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:14:\"Editorial Team\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:17071:\"<p>Are you looking for the best WordPress quiz plugins? Great idea! Quizzes are a great way to drive traffic to your website and increase user engagement.</p>\n<p>In this article, we’ll introduce you to the 11 best WordPress quiz plugins on the market.</p>\n<h3>Why Use a Quiz Plugin?</h3>\n<p>Quizzes can be a fun and effective part of your marketing strategy. By utilizing one of the best WordPress quiz plugins, you can quickly and easily craft a professional-looking quiz for your website.</p>\n<p>Online audiences are addicted to quizzes. If you embed a quiz onto your <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/how-to-make-a-website-step-by-step/\">WordPress site</a> as a page feature or as part of a blog post, you’ll have an attention-grabbing device at your disposal to drive additional traffic your way.</p>\n<p>As a general rule, people tend to be self-absorbed, and quizzes play into this mentality. Provided your quizzes aren’t too long (the modern populace also has a short attention span!), you can tap into your website visitors’ psychological need to self-evaluate.</p>\n<p>Quizzes also tap into our human need to share and compare aspects of ourselves with others. This is a main element of why quizzes make for great marketing! Quizzes are insanely shareable. So, not only will users stay and engage with the quiz while on your site, they’ll share their results, with a link back to your site, to send more traffic your way.</p>\n<p>With the best WordPress quiz plugins at your disposal, you can use this marketing strategy to your advantage with shockingly good results. The ROI (return on investment) for purchasing a quiz plugin is extremely high.</p>\n<p>That said, are you ready to check out the best WordPress quiz plugins? Awesome. Let’s get started.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wpforms.com/\" target=\"_blank\">1. WPForms</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wpforms.com/\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/WPForms.jpg\" alt=\"WPForms\" width=\"775\" height=\"221\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-222917\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/WPForms.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/WPForms-300x86.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/WPForms-768x219.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>You may recognize WPForms as one of the <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-contact-form-plugins/\">best contact forms plugin</a> for WordPress. But did you know it can also be used to create surveys and polls?</p>\n<p>You’ll need WPForms’ Pro plan in order to use their surveys and polls addon. Fortunately, IsItWP users can get 10% off the total price when they use the coupon code <strong>SAVE10</strong>.</p>\n<p>With a little manipulation behind-the-scenes, WPForms’ surveys and polls addon can be transformed into a one-of-a-kind quiz for your website. Embedding is easy, and your quiz can be placed on a post, page, or widget-ready area.</p>\n<p>WPForms’ intuitive drag and drop builder makes it easy to build and customize a quiz that’s sure to blow your audience away!</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wpforms.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Get Started with WPForms Today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/tryinteract/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">2. TryInteract</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/tryinteract/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/TryInteract.jpg\" alt=\"TryInteract\" width=\"775\" height=\"287\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-222989\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/TryInteract.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/TryInteract-300x111.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/TryInteract-768x284.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>With over 200 pre-built templates in 37 different niches, TryInteract makes it simple to create a custom quiz specifically for your website.</p>\n<p>You’ll have control over all your quizzes’ colors, fonts, images, and logos. Building a quiz that matches your brand has never been easier.</p>\n<p>You can also use TryInteract to capture leads and convert them into subscribers by having an optin option at the end of each quiz. Don’t want just anyone joining your list? No problem. You can segment your audience and convert only users who’ve scored 50 percent or higher on your quiz.</p>\n<p>Best of all? TryInteract quizzes are <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/how-to-make-a-wordpress-privacy-policy/\">fully GDPR compliant</a> and the company itself is registered with Privacy Shield. Your users will feel safe answering your questions, and you’ll be recognized as a trusted site owner.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/tryinteract/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get Started with TryInteract Today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/learndash/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">3. LearnDash</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/learndash/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/LearnDash.png\" alt=\"LearnDash\" width=\"775\" height=\"375\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-222990\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/LearnDash.png 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/LearnDash-300x145.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/LearnDash-768x372.png 768w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/LearnDash-330x160.png 330w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>LearnDash is one of our favorite <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-lms-plugins-compared/\">LMS (learning management system) plugins</a>. Part of what puts it ahead of the crowd is its interactive quiz feature.</p>\n<p>If you have a membership site or online course and want to quiz your users, LearnDash is the perfect plugin for the job.</p>\n<p>Not only will you be able to quiz your users, you’ll also be able to grade their answers and award them badges for successful completion. By making your users feel good about themselves, you’ll increase further engagement exponentially.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/learndash/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get Started with LearnDash Today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/polldaddy/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">4. Polldaddy</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/polldaddy/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/Polldaddy.jpg\" alt=\"Polldaddy\" width=\"775\" height=\"286\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-222991\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/Polldaddy.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/Polldaddy-300x111.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/Polldaddy-768x283.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Quiz me, Daddy! Polldaddy is one of the best WordPress quiz plugins because it was created by Automattic, the company behind WordPress.com and the progenitors of plugins.</p>\n<p>Not only are Polldaddy quizzes highly customizable and easy to create via their advanced editor, you can also access in-depth reports of your users’ engagements with them. Plus, those reports can be exported in CSV, Excel, PDF, Google Docs, and XML formats.</p>\n<p>You can add images and videos, including content from YouTube, Flickr, or Google Maps.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/polldaddy/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get started with Polldaddy Today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/wp-quiz/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">5. WP Quiz</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/wp-quiz/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/WPQuiz.png\" alt=\"WP Quiz\" width=\"775\" height=\"248\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-222992\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/WPQuiz.png 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/WPQuiz-300x96.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/WPQuiz-768x246.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Easy to use and 100 percent free, WP Quiz is a great option, especially if you’re on a tight budget.</p>\n<p>You can use WP Quiz with virtually any WordPress theme, and create an unlimited number of quizzes for your audience. Quiz types include trivia quizzes, personality quizzes, and flip quizzes. All of which can be configured for single or multi-page layouts.</p>\n<p>WP Quiz allows you to customize the fonts, background colors, and progress bars for each quiz you build. And they’re simple to add to your posts and pages via the shortcode support.</p>\n<p>Last, your quizzes will be highly shareable thanks to the social share buttons included with the plugin.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/wp-quiz/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get Started with WP Quiz Today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/quiz-master-next/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">6. Quiz and Survey Master</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/quiz-master-next/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/wordpress-quizzes-and-survey.png\" alt=\"wordpress quizzes and survey\" width=\"740\" height=\"269\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-224249\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/wordpress-quizzes-and-survey.png 740w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/wordpress-quizzes-and-survey-300x109.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 740px) 100vw, 740px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Formerly known as Quiz Master Next, the Quiz and Survey Master plugin is perfect for business owners. You can easily create quizzes to gauge employee satisfaction or gather customer feedback.</p>\n<p>If you want to limit the number of people who take your quiz, you can set Quiz and Survey Master to only show quizzes to logged-in users. You can also schedule when quizzes are active on your site. Or, to further limit over-usage of your quizzes, you can set the amount of attempts a user has to complete a quiz.</p>\n<p>For math buffs, you’ll be happy to know that you can create and display complex mathematical formulas using Quiz and Survey Master. This makes it perfect for math-based online courses or mentoring programs.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/quiz-master-next/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get Started with Quiz and Survey Master Today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/mtouch-quiz/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">7. mTouch Quiz</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/mtouch-quiz/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/mTouchQuiz.png\" alt=\"mTouch Quiz\" width=\"775\" height=\"256\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-222994\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/mTouchQuiz.png 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/mTouchQuiz-300x99.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/mTouchQuiz-768x254.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>It’s all in the name: mTouch Quiz is a touch-friendly plugin. Meaning, it’s great for mobile or tablet quizzes in which users touch their screens to select their answers.</p>\n<p>mTouch Quiz is quick and easy to use, and you can even create custom start and finish pages to dazzle your users with.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/mtouch-quiz/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get Started with mTouch Quiz Today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/ari-stream-quiz/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">8. ARI Stream Quiz</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/ari-stream-quiz/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/ARIStreamQuiz.png\" alt=\"ARI Stream Quiz\" width=\"775\" height=\"234\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-222995\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/ARIStreamQuiz.png 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/ARIStreamQuiz-300x91.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/ARIStreamQuiz-768x232.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>If you’re looking for a quiz plugin to gain additional leads, then ARI Steam Quiz is a great choice.</p>\n<p>This plugin integrates with MailChimp, AWeber, ConstantContact, Drip, and many other email marketing services. It also integrates with popular email services, Facebook, Twitter, Pinterest, LinkedIn, and other social networks for easy sharing.</p>\n<p>ARI Stream Quiz is also translation-ready so you can communicate with users from all over the world.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/ari-stream-quiz/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get Started with ARI Stream Quiz Today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/chained-quiz/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">9. Chained Quiz</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/chained-quiz/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/ChainedQuiz.jpg\" alt=\"Chained Quiz\" width=\"775\" height=\"349\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-222996\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/ChainedQuiz.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/ChainedQuiz-300x135.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/ChainedQuiz-768x346.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Using conditional logic, you can build a “chained” quiz in which the next question depends on the previous answer submitted by the user.</p>\n<p>Chained Quiz is perfect for essay-style questions. You can even assign point values to grade the user’s answers.</p>\n<p>For added value, Chained Quiz allows you to export users’ answers into a CSV file so that you can analyze their results in Excel.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/chained-quiz/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get Started with Chained Quiz Today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/hd-quiz/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">10. HD Quiz</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/hd-quiz/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/HDQuiz.png\" alt=\"HD Quiz\" width=\"775\" height=\"255\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-222997\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/HDQuiz.png 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/HDQuiz-300x99.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/HDQuiz-768x253.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Featured images, including animated GIFs, are a big part of what makes HD Quiz special. It’s a very visual quiz-building plugin. You can even use images as answers!</p>\n<p>Build an unlimited amount of mobile-friendly quizzes with this free plugin. It’s fun and easy to use, and will create quizzes for your website akin to what you might see on Buzzfeed.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/hd-quiz/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get Started with HD Quiz Today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/quiz-cat/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">11. Quiz Cat</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/quiz-cat/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/QuizCat.png\" alt=\"Quiz Cat\" width=\"775\" height=\"266\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-222998\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/QuizCat.png 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/QuizCat-300x103.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/QuizCat-768x264.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Curiosity won’t kill this cat! Quiz Cat encourages curious users to engage with customized quizzes embedded on your WordPress posts and pages.</p>\n<p>Create an unlimited number of multiple-choice quizzes. To keep users guessing, Quiz Cat randomly shuffles the answers to each question so they’re never in the same order. No cheating THIS cat!</p>\n<p>Translation-ready and embeddable via shortcodes, Quiz Cat is a great free tool and definitely one of the best WordPress quiz plugins.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/quiz-cat/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get Started with Quiz Cat Today!</a></p>\n<p>We hope this article helped you discover the best WordPress Quiz plugins.</p>\n<p>If you enjoyed this post, you might like our step-by-step guide on <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/create-a-survey-in-wordpress/\">how to easily create a survey in WordPress</a>.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-quiz-plugins/\">11 Best WordPress Quiz Plugins to Boost User Engagement</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com\">IsItWP - WordPress Technology Lookup Tool</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:56:\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-quiz-plugins/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:4;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:54:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n		\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:59:\"How to Secure Your WordPress Forms with Password Protection\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:66:\"https://www.isitwp.com/secure-wordpress-forms-password-protection/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:74:\"https://www.isitwp.com/secure-wordpress-forms-password-protection/#respond\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Mon, 05 Nov 2018 12:41:09 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:5:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:19:\"WordPress Tutorials\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"best form plugins for wordpress\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:2;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:8:\"password\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:3;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:11:\"secure form\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:4;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:7:\"wpforms\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:32:\"https://www.isitwp.com/?p=223555\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:638:\"<p>Wondering how to secure your WordPress forms with password protection? If so, you came to the right place. With the right forms plugin and the proper know-how, you can quickly and easily add password protection to your WordPress forms. In this article, we’ll share how to secure your WordPress forms with password protection the EASY [&#8230;]</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/secure-wordpress-forms-password-protection/\">How to Secure Your WordPress Forms with Password Protection</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com\">IsItWP - WordPress Technology Lookup Tool</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:14:\"Editorial Team\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:12397:\"<p>Wondering how to secure your WordPress forms with password protection? If so, you came to the right place. With the right forms plugin and the proper know-how, you can quickly and easily add password protection to your WordPress forms.</p>\n<p>In this article, we’ll share how to secure your WordPress forms with password protection the EASY way.</p>\n<h3>Password Protect Your Form with WPForms</h3>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/wpforms.png\" alt=\"WPForms\" width=\"775\" height=\"350\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-218485\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/wpforms.png 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/wpforms-300x135.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/wpforms-768x347.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></p>\n<p>If you’re going to have forms on your <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/how-to-make-a-website-step-by-step/\">WordPress website</a>, then we recommend using the <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-contact-form-plugins/\">absolute best forms plugin</a> on the market: <a href=\"https://wpforms.com\" target=\"_blank\">WPForms</a>.</p>\n<p>If you’re asking about how to secure your WordPress forms with password protection, you’re probably looking to avoid getting unwanted form submissions. If that’s the case, then <a href=\"https://wpforms.com\" target=\"_blank\">WPForms</a> is the perfect choice for you.</p>\n<p>Not only does <a href=\"https://wpforms.com\" target=\"_blank\">WPForms</a> have a Post Submissions addon, which will allow you to get submissions in the first place; it’s also incredibly easy to add password protection to.</p>\n<p>Adding password protection to your <a href=\"https://wpforms.com\" target=\"_blank\">WPForms</a> submission forms will save you from wasting time reviewing content you don’t intend to use. Only those with access will be able to send you content.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wpforms.com\" target=\"_blank\">WPForms</a> features an intuitive drag and drop builder, making it easy to use and beginner-friendly, even when creating advanced forms. It comes with GDPR enhancements so that you can be compliant, even when asking for others’ valuable information.</p>\n<p>IsItWP readers can save 10 percent off the cost of WPForms Pro by using the coupon code <strong>SAVE10</strong>.</p>\n<p>Once you’ve purchased the <a href=\"https://wpforms.com\" target=\"_blank\">WPForms</a> plugin, follow our 4-step guide below on how to secure your WordPress forms with password protection.</p>\n<h3>Step 1: Install WPForms on Your Website</h3>\n<p>From your WordPress dashboard, scroll down to Plugins on the left-hand side. Click the Add New button.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/add-new-plugin.png\" alt=\"add new plugin\" width=\"775\" height=\"235\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-223559\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/add-new-plugin.png 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/add-new-plugin-300x91.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/add-new-plugin-768x233.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></p>\n<p>From there, click the <strong>Upload Plugin</strong> button.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/upload-new-plugin.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"775\" height=\"222\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-223560\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/upload-new-plugin.png 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/upload-new-plugin-300x86.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/upload-new-plugin-768x220.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></p>\n<p>Upload the .zip file you downloaded from the WPForms website. Note: If you haven’t downloaded your plugin and addons from WPForms, you can find them in your Account section on <a href=\"https://wpforms.com\" target=\"_blank\">their website</a>.</p>\n<p>Once the plugin has been uploaded, click the <strong>Activate</strong> button.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/activate-wpforms-plugin.png\" alt=\"activate WPForms plugin\" width=\"775\" height=\"331\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-223561\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/activate-wpforms-plugin.png 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/activate-wpforms-plugin-300x128.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/activate-wpforms-plugin-768x328.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></p>\n<p>Now, go to the newly-added WPForms tab on your dashboard’s navigation bar. Head to <strong>WPForms » Settings</strong>.</p>\n<p>Enter your license key in the appropriate field to gain access to all of WPForms Pro’s features. You can find your license key in your Account section on the WPForms website. Simply copy and paste it into the field.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/wpforms-license-key.png\" alt=\"WPForms license key\" width=\"775\" height=\"308\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-223562\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/wpforms-license-key.png 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/wpforms-license-key-300x119.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/wpforms-license-key-768x305.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></p>\n<p>Your plugin is now ready to rock and roll. You have basic form-building capabilities.</p>\n<p>Now, it’s time to kick it up a notch.</p>\n<h3>Step 2: Activate Your Addons</h3>\n<p>There&#8217;re 2 addons you’ll need to activate: <strong>Post Submissions</strong> and <strong>Form Locker</strong>. The first will allow you to accept content submissions from your visitors, while the second is needed to secure your form.</p>\n<p>First, head to <strong>WPForms » Addons</strong>.</p>\n<p>Locate the <strong>Post Submissions</strong> and <strong>Form Locker</strong> addons and install them by clicking the Install button.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/install-addon.png\" alt=\"install addon\" width=\"775\" height=\"307\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-223563\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/install-addon.png 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/install-addon-300x119.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/install-addon-768x304.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></p>\n<p>Once installed, make sure the addons are activated. Hit the activation toggle.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/activate-addon.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"379\" height=\"302\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-223564\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/activate-addon.png 379w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/activate-addon-300x239.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 379px) 100vw, 379px\" /></p>\n<p>It will turn green and say “Active” if you’ve successfully activated it.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/active-status.png\" alt=\"active status\" width=\"369\" height=\"294\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-223565\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/active-status.png 369w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/active-status-300x239.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 369px) 100vw, 369px\" /></p>\n<p>You’re good to go! It’s time to build your first form.</p>\n<h3>Step 3: Create a WordPress Form</h3>\n<p>On your dashboard, head to <strong>WPForms » Add New</strong>.</p>\n<p>Once the WPForms editor appears, scroll down and find the <strong>Blog Submissions Form</strong> template and click on it.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/create-submission-form.png\" alt=\"create submission form\" width=\"773\" height=\"317\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-223566\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/create-submission-form.png 773w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/create-submission-form-300x123.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/create-submission-form-768x315.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 773px) 100vw, 773px\" /></p>\n<p>A form for accepting blog posts will appear:</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/modify-submission-form.png\" alt=\"modify submission form\" width=\"775\" height=\"325\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-223567\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/modify-submission-form.png 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/modify-submission-form-300x126.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/modify-submission-form-768x322.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></p>\n<p>Feel free to drag and drop fields to your heart’s content. Get it looking exactly how you need it to, and then click <strong>Save</strong>.</p>\n<h3>Step 4: Enable Password Protection</h3>\n<p>To enable password protection on your submissions form, you’ll be utilizing the Form Locker addon you activated.</p>\n<p>While still in the form editor, go to <strong>Settings » Form Locker</strong>.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/form-locker-settings.png\" alt=\"form locker settings\" width=\"562\" height=\"359\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-223568\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/form-locker-settings.png 562w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/form-locker-settings-300x192.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 562px) 100vw, 562px\" /></p>\n<p>Check the <strong>Enable Password Protection</strong> box under the Password section.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/form-locker-password-protection.png\" alt=\"form locker password protection\" width=\"562\" height=\"333\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-223570\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/form-locker-password-protection.png 562w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/form-locker-password-protection-300x178.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 562px) 100vw, 562px\" /></p>\n<p>From there, you can configure the 2 password settings that appear. For <strong>Password</strong>, you can choose the password you want users to enter to access your submissions form. For <strong>Display Message</strong>, type what you want to appear above the password field so your users know they need a password in order to submit their content.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/password-settings.png\" alt=\"password settings\" width=\"562\" height=\"355\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-223569\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/password-settings.png 562w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/password-settings-300x190.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 562px) 100vw, 562px\" /></p>\n<p>Upon finishing, slick <strong>Save</strong>.</p>\n<p>Once your form is live on your site, this message (or whatever you wrote) will appear for your users:</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/final-password-protected-form.png\" alt=\"final password protected form\" width=\"562\" height=\"235\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-223571\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/final-password-protected-form.png 562w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/final-password-protected-form-300x125.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 562px) 100vw, 562px\" /></p>\n<p>After the user enters the correct password, the submission form will appear and they’ll be able to send you their content.</p>\n<p>Your submission form is officially password protected!</p>\n<p>We hope this article helped you learn how to secure your WordPress forms with password protection.</p>\n<p>If you liked this post, you might also love our tutorial on <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/custom-user-registration-form-wordpress/\" title=\"How to Create a Custom User Registration Form in WordPress\">how to create a custom user registration form in WordPress</a>.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/secure-wordpress-forms-password-protection/\">How to Secure Your WordPress Forms with Password Protection</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com\">IsItWP - WordPress Technology Lookup Tool</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:71:\"https://www.isitwp.com/secure-wordpress-forms-password-protection/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:5;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:39:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:6:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:58:\"WPML Review: Is It the Best WordPresss Translation Plugin?\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:46:\"https://www.isitwp.com/wordpress-plugins/wpml/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:54:\"https://www.isitwp.com/wordpress-plugins/wpml/#respond\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Fri, 02 Nov 2018 13:50:33 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:56:\"https://www.isitwp.com/?post_type=isitwp_plugin&p=224011\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:651:\"<p>Want to make your WordPress site multilingual to allow your users to read your website content in their preferred language? If you&#8217;ve conducted any research, you likely found WPML plugin recommended by several well-renowned blogs. WPML is certainly a popular WordPress translation plugin; however, it isn’t prudent to purchase a premium plugin without reading a [&#8230;]</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wordpress-plugins/wpml/\">WPML Review: Is It the Best WordPresss Translation Plugin?</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com\">IsItWP - WordPress Technology Lookup Tool</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:14:\"Editorial Team\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:14224:\"<p>Want to make your WordPress site multilingual to allow your users to read your website content in their preferred language? If you&#8217;ve conducted any research, you likely found WPML plugin recommended by several well-renowned blogs. WPML is certainly a popular WordPress translation plugin; however, it isn’t prudent to purchase a premium plugin without reading a proper in-depth analysis. </p>\n<p>In this WPML review, we’ll dig deeper into its features, functionalities, pricing, and more to help you decide if it&#8217;s the right plugin for you.</p>\n<h3>About WPML Plugin</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/wpml/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/wpml-plugin-reviewed.jpg\" alt=\"wpml-plugin-reviewed\" width=\"775\" height=\"365\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-224013\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/wpml-plugin-reviewed.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/wpml-plugin-reviewed-300x141.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/wpml-plugin-reviewed-768x362.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/wpml/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">The WordPress Multilingual Plugin (WPML)</a> is the most <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/top-wordpress-plugins/\">popular WordPress plugin</a> for <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/easily-create-multilingual-wordpress-website/\">creating a multilingual website</a>. WPML allows you to easily translate your WordPress content into multiple languages and run them smoothly on your site. </p>\n<p>Using WPML, you can manage different language contents in the same domain with a single WordPress installation. This helps you to serve a diverse audience from a single website without having to install WordPress on multiple domains. </p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/wpml/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">WPML plugin</a> works with almost all <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/top-wordpress-themes/\">WordPress themes</a> and <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/top-wordpress-plugins/\">plugins</a> available on the market. It’s SEO friendly and lets you choose language URL format as directories, subdomains, or parameters. Plus, it works with the Yoast SEO plugin and other SEO-related plugins well. </p>\n<p>WPML is created and managed by OnTheGoSystems. The plugin has available for a long time now, yet they still offer regular updates and dedicated support to their customers. </p>\n<h3>Why Create a Multilingual WordPress Site?</h3>\n<p>By creating a <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/how-to-make-a-website-step-by-step/\">WordPress website</a>, you make your content accessible to people living across the world but are all of the world&#8217;s internet users really able to enjoy it? Probably not. That&#8217;s because language causes a major barrier!</p>\n<p>While it&#8217;s nearly impossible to make your site available in ALL the languages spoken in the world, you can definitely make it accessible for the languages most-used by your visitors. Adding additional language translations to your site makes your site more user-friendly and ensures more users turn into customers. </p>\n<p>By <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/easily-create-multilingual-wordpress-website/\">creating a multilingual website</a>, you can easily reach out to a wider audience. Businesses aiming for an international market especially need to consider making their site multilingual. </p>\n<h3>WPML Review: Getting Started with WPML</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/wpml/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">WPML</a> is a simple and easy-to-use plugin that you can quickly configure to make your site multilingual. </p>\n<p>After you install and activate the plugin, it’ll guide you through the configuration process with a step-by-step setup wizard. </p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/wpml-setup-wizard.jpg\" alt=\"wpml-setup-wizard\" width=\"775\" height=\"435\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-221125\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/wpml-setup-wizard.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/wpml-setup-wizard-300x168.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/wpml-setup-wizard-768x431.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></p>\n<p>First, it’ll automatically detect your site&#8217;s current language. You can proceed to the next step if you don’t want to change that. </p>\n<p>In the second step, you can choose the languages you want to enable on your site. </p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/select-languages-wpml-setup.jpg\" alt=\"select-languages-wpml-setup\" width=\"775\" height=\"435\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-221126\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/select-languages-wpml-setup.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/select-languages-wpml-setup-300x168.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/select-languages-wpml-setup-768x431.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></p>\n<p>The third step allows you to configure and customize the language switcher options. </p>\n<p>You can arrange the order of the languages and add the language switcher to the navigation menu, widget area, or footer area on your site. You can choose the language switcher style (dropdown or list of languages), what to include in the language switcher (flag, language name, current language), change language switcher&#8217;s color, etc. </p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/wpml-language-switcher-options.jpg\" alt=\"wpml-language-switcher-options\" width=\"775\" height=\"372\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-221127\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/wpml-language-switcher-options.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/wpml-language-switcher-options-300x144.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/wpml-language-switcher-options-768x369.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></p>\n<p>After you configure the language switcher options in step 3, you’ll need to enter your site key to register for automatic plugin updates. You can find the key in your account on <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/wpml/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">WPML&#8217;s website</a>. </p>\n<p>Once the setup process is completed, you’ll be all set to start translating your WordPress content. </p>\n<h3>WordPress Translation Made Easy</h3>\n<p>Using <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/wpml/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">WPML</a>, you can translate almost everything inside your WordPress dashboard. It allows you to translate WordPress posts, pages, custom post types, tags, categories, custom fields, and content created with page builders, as well as theme and plugin texts. </p>\n<p>To start translating your posts, go to <strong>Posts &raquo; All Posts</strong>. There you’ll see your total posts, and the number of posts per language. </p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/translate-button-all-posts.jpg\" alt=\"translate-button-all-posts\" width=\"775\" height=\"328\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-221131\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/translate-button-all-posts.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/translate-button-all-posts-300x127.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/translate-button-all-posts-768x325.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></p>\n<p>Additionally, you&#8217;ll see <strong>Add</strong> buttons for each language you selected next to your post. You can start the translation process by clicking on 1 of them. </p>\n<p>Then, it’ll open a new post editor with the language name or flag (or both) at the top and a <strong>Language Meta box</strong> on the right side. </p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/new-traslation-post.jpg\" alt=\"new-traslation-post-wpml\" width=\"775\" height=\"483\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-221132\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/new-traslation-post.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/new-traslation-post-300x187.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/new-traslation-post-768x479.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></p>\n<p>Now, you can add the translated content to the post area and publish. However, if you aren’t able to translate for any reason, you can use other translation options. </p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/wpml/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">WPML</a> comes with a powerful <strong>Translation Management addon</strong> which allows you to work with a team of translators and translation services. With this addon, you can add professional translators of your own or use third-party translation services (or both) on your site. </p>\n<h3>WPML Addons</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/wpml/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">WPML</a> comes with a suite of addons along with the core plugin, </strong>WPML Multilingual CMS</strong>. Installing the core plugin is always necessary, whereas you can choose to install other addons as per your requirements. </p>\n<p>Some of the most useful WPML addons are: </p>\n<p><strong>1. WPML Translation Management</strong></p>\n<p>You can properly manage translation on your site with this addon. You can add your own translators, give them a <strong>Translator</strong> role, and assign them translation work. You can also use different translation services as WPML integrates with the web’s leading translation services.</p>\n<p><strong>2. WPML String Translation</strong></p>\n<p>This addon lets you translate interface strings directly from within WordPress without using .mo files. You can translate not just static texts, but also user-generated texts outside posts including the tagline and SEO data.</p>\n<p><strong>3. WPML Media Translation</strong></p>\n<p>With this addon, you can use your WordPress media gallery in different languages. It lets you control which images to display for each language.</p>\n<p><strong>4. WooCommerce Multilingual</strong></p>\n<p>Using this addon, you can build a multilingual eCommerce site. It allows you to translate all of your WooCommerce content including products, variations, categories, fields, and attributes easily.</p>\n<p><strong>5. BuddyPress Multilingual</strong></p>\n<p>You can translate your BuddyPress website and create a multilingual social network site with this addon. </p>\n<p>You can learn about all of WPML&#8217;s addons by visiting the official <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/wpml/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">WPML website</a>. </p>\n<h3>WPML Plugin: Pricing and Support</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/wpml/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">WPML</a> is a premium plugin with 3 pricing options: <strong>Multilingual Blog</strong>, <strong>Multilingual CMS</strong>, and <strong>Multilingual Agency</strong>. </p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/wpml/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/wpml-pricing.jpg\" alt=\"wpml-pricing\" width=\"775\" height=\"580\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-224016\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/wpml-pricing.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/wpml-pricing-300x225.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/wpml-pricing-768x575.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>The pricing plans are actually the different combinations of the core WPML plugin with addons. </p>\n<p>First plan, <strong>Multilingual Blog</strong>, is an economic solution for multilingual WordPress blogs with basic translation controls and few addons. This plan allows you to install WPML on only 1 site. You can buy this for $29. </p>\n<p>Second plan, <strong>Multilingual CMS</strong>, is a complete solution for multilingual WordPress sites that comes packed with all the available addons. It comes with 3 site licenses. It&#8217;s available at $79. </p>\n<p>The third plan, <strong>Multilingual Agency</strong>, is an unlimited license plan suitable for agencies building many sites. It comes with the same features and addons provided in the CMS plan. Its price is $159. So, you can choose either CMS or Agency plan for advanced translation features, depending on the number of sites you want to use WPML on. </p>\n<p>All the plans come with 1 year of free updates and premium support. If the plugin fails to work as promised, you can claim a refund within 30 days of purchase. </p>\n<h3>Our Verdict on Using WPML Plugin on Your Site</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/wpml/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">WPML</a> is the most advanced and feature-rich WordPress multilingual plugin available on the market. It offers a host of powerful features to allow you to completely translate your WordPress site into multiple languages. </p>\n<p>The plugin interface is simple and user-friendly. The idea of addons is cool as you can install only the ones you actually need. That way, you can keep your site lightweight. </p>\n<p>Moreover, it’s compatible with any WordPress theme and plugins so you can freely install your favorite web applications on your site and translate them. It’s an SEO-friendly plugin which makes your site look good to both humans and search engine bots. </p>\n<p>We believe that <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/wpml/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">WPML</a> is certainly the best WordPress translation plugin for creating a multilingual site. It’s the perfect choice for all types of multilingual websites including a blog, business, eCommerce site, or social networking site. </p>\n<p>We give it 4.5 out of 5 stars. Here’s the breakdown of our review score:</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wordpress-plugins/wpml/\">WPML Review: Is It the Best WordPresss Translation Plugin?</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com\">IsItWP - WordPress Technology Lookup Tool</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:51:\"https://www.isitwp.com/wordpress-plugins/wpml/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:6;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:57:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:52:\"9 Best WordPress Real Estate Plugins COMPARED (2018)\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:58:\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-real-estate-plugins/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:66:\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-real-estate-plugins/#respond\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Thu, 01 Nov 2018 07:54:28 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:6:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:17:\"WordPress Plugins\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:24:\"best real estate plugins\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:2;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:34:\"best wordpress real estate plugins\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:3;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:19:\"real estate plugins\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:4;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:29:\"real estate wordpress plugins\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:5;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:21:\"wordpress real estate\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:32:\"https://www.isitwp.com/?p=223537\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:612:\"<p>Do you want the best real estate plugins for your WordPress website? Real estate websites are a fantastic business generator as they support tools and features to make property deals online. In this article, we&#8217;ll share 9 of the best WordPress real estate plugins you can use to make your website a success. Creating a [&#8230;]</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-real-estate-plugins/\">9 Best WordPress Real Estate Plugins COMPARED (2018)</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com\">IsItWP - WordPress Technology Lookup Tool</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:14:\"Editorial Team\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:17619:\"<p>Do you want the best real estate plugins for your WordPress website? Real estate websites are a fantastic business generator as they support tools and features to make property deals online.</p>\n<p>In this article, we&#8217;ll share 9 of the best WordPress real estate plugins you can use to make your website a success.</p>\n<h3>Creating a Real Estate Website with WordPress</h3>\n<p>WordPress is the most flexible and popular website builder on the market. Many of <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/popular-big-name-brands-using-wordpress/\" title=\"46 Biggest Brands in the World Using WordPress Actively\">the world&#8217;s top brands are using WordPress</a> for their websites.</p>\n<p>You&#8217;ll find 2 kinds of WordPress websites: WordPress.com, which is a hosted platform; and WordPress.org, which is a self-hosted solution. For more details, see our side-by-side comparison on <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wordpress-com-vs-wordpress-org-one-really-better/\" title=\"WordPress.com vs. WordPress.org – Is One Really Better Than the Other?\">WordPress.com vs WordPress.org</a>.</p>\n<p>For a real estate website, you should use self-hosted WordPress.org. It&#8217;s highly flexible and offers amazing features to develop powerful websites.</p>\n<p>Before starting, you&#8217;ll need to buy a domain name and a web hosting account to install WordPress properly.</p>\n<p>Bluehost is our recommended web hosting solution. It&#8217;s one of the most popular hosting companies and is officially recommended by WordPress&#8217; core.</p>\n<p>Luckily, they&#8217;re offering IsItWP readers a free domain name, free SSL certificate, and a massive discount on web hosting.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/create-a-wordpress-account-on-bluehost.jpg\" alt=\"create a blog on bluehost\" width=\"775\" height=\"483\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-218254\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/create-a-wordpress-account-on-bluehost.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/create-a-wordpress-account-on-bluehost-300x187.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/create-a-wordpress-account-on-bluehost-768x479.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/bluehost/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"btn ltgreen light\">Click Here to Claim This Exclusive Bluehost Offer &raquo;</a></p>\n<p>After purchasing web hosting, you can follow our step-by-step guide on <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/how-to-make-a-website-step-by-step/\" title=\"How to Make a Website in 2018- Step by Step (with Pictures)\">how to create a WordPress website</a>.</p>\n<p>Having said that, let&#8217;s take a look at the best WordPress real estate plugins.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/real-estate-pro/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Real Estate Pro\" rel=\"nofollow\">1. Real Estate Pro</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/real-estate-pro/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Real Estate Pro\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/realestatepro.jpg\" alt=\"Real Estate Pro\" width=\"775\" height=\"300\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-223541\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/realestatepro.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/realestatepro-300x116.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/realestatepro-768x297.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Real Estate Pro is a premium WordPress real estate and property listing plugin. It enables your users to add their listings, claim listings, sell properties, manage client reviews, and more. Your website&#8217;s visitors can bid for the properties, leave a note for the listing owner, contact property owners, and <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/tips-get-email-subscribers/\" title=\"23 Effective Tips to Get More Email Subscribers Today\">subscribe to your lists</a> to get regular updates.</p>\n<p>The plugin&#8217;s translation-ready and fully supports <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/wpml/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"WPML\" rel=\"nofollow\">WPML</a>. It also supports third-party services like Stripe, PayPal, <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/mailchimp/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"MailChimp\" rel=\"nofollow\">MailChimp</a>, etc. </p>\n<p>Real Estate Pro is integrated with <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/visual-composer-website-builder/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Visual Composer\" rel=\"nofollow\">Visual Composer</a> to quickly set up your property website and <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/legit-ways-to-make-money-online-blogging/\" title=\"30 Ways to Make Money Online Blogging (On the Side) in 2018\">start making money online</a>.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/estatik/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Estatik\" rel=\"nofollow\">2. Estatik</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/estatik/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Estatik\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/estatik.jpg\" alt=\"Estatik\" width=\"775\" height=\"300\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-223540\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/estatik.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/estatik-300x116.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/estatik-768x297.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Estatik is a free WordPress real estate plugin that can be used to add property listings on your website. You can use this plugin to create and manage fully functional real estate solutions with ease.</p>\n<p>It offers language support, <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wordpress-plugins/google-maps-builder/\" title=\"Google Maps Builder Review: Easily Embed Interactive Maps\">Google Maps</a> integration, <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-social-media-plugins/\" title=\"12 Best WordPress Social Media Plugins (2018)\">social media</a> icons, <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-gallery-plugins-compared/\" title=\"7 Best WordPress Gallery Plugins Compared (2018)\">an image gallery</a>, real estate widget, and more. It comes with unlimited options for your property listings so you can customize and sell the properties online.</p>\n<p>Estatik has advanced filters in the search for dates, famous properties, pricing, and location. It&#8217;s a fully customizable plugin and works great with all the <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/top-wordpress-themes/\" title=\"The Best and Most Popular WordPress Themes of 2018 (UPDATED)\">top WordPress themes</a>.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/wp-listings/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"IMPress Listings\" rel=\"nofollow\">3. IMPress Listings</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/wp-listings/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"IMPress Listings\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/impresslistings.jpg\" alt=\"IMPress listings\" width=\"775\" height=\"300\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-223542\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/impresslistings.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/impresslistings-300x116.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/impresslistings-768x297.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>IMPress Listings is a popular WordPress plugin for real estate websites. It offers a complete solution for beginners to advanced users to launch an online real estate business.</p>\n<p>It allows your users to add their listings with images and videos of the properties. The visual impact increases traffic on your real estate website and helps with <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-seo-tools-to-grow-your-site-traffic/\" title=\"9 Best SEO Tools to Grow Your Website Traffic, FAST!\">improving SEO</a>. You can easily customize the property listings and design beautiful listing pages with complete details, Google maps, and contact information of the listing&#8217;s owner.</p>\n<p>It fully supports IDX listing and you can also import listings from other sources. It recommends a few companion plugins to include additional features to make a truly powerful real estate website.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/wp-amortization-calculator/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"WP Amortization Calculator\" rel=\"nofollow\">4. WP Amortization Calculator</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/wp-amortization-calculator/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"WP Amortization Calculator\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/wpamortizationcalc.jpg\" alt=\"WP Amortization Calculator\" width=\"775\" height=\"300\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-223544\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/wpamortizationcalc.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/wpamortizationcalc-300x116.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/wpamortizationcalc-768x297.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>WP Amortization Calculator is a premium WordPress plugin used to calculate mortgages, loans, and property financing online. It has features go above and beyond a simple mortgage calculator. It supports a lead capture tool, real estate listings, agents portal, custom property pages, email notifications, and more.</p>\n<p>It also enables you to use currency symbols and different money format choices. The <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-page-builders-compared/\" title=\"7 Best Drag and Drop WordPress Page Builders Compared (2018)\">drag and drop builder</a> support allows you to add a sophisticated amortization calculator anywhere on your real estate website.</p>\n<p>It has a custom widget that can be added in your widget areas. It&#8217;s translation-ready and includes flexible options to automatically calculate amortized loans.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/wp-property/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"WP-Property\" rel=\"nofollow\">5. WP-Property</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/wp-property/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"WP-Property\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/wpproperty.jpg\" alt=\"WP Property\" width=\"775\" height=\"300\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-223545\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/wpproperty.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/wpproperty-300x116.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/wpproperty-768x297.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>WP-Property is a free real estate WordPress plugin. It has the options to add property listings, manage listings, and more. It includes powerful custom options to add complete details for each property listing, like yhe number of rooms, bathrooms, capacity, parking, and other features of the property.</p>\n<p>You can create stylish property listing pages with Google Maps, real estate search, featured listings, search filters, and <a href=\"https://www.wpbeginner.com/wp-tutorials/how-to-create-an-idx-real-estate-website-using-wordpress/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"IDX listing support\">IDX listing support</a>. It suggests free WordPress real estate themes and also works great with all other themes.</p>\n<p>It has widgets, shortcodes, and other methods to show real estate listings anywhere on your WordPress website. WP-Property is a flexible plugin with translation support and it&#8217;s optimized for SEO.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/essential-real-estate/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Essential Real Estate\" rel=\"nofollow\">6. Essential Real Estate</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/essential-real-estate/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Essential Real Estate\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/essentialrealestate.jpg\" alt=\"Essential real estate\" width=\"775\" height=\"300\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-223547\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/essentialrealestate.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/essentialrealestate-300x116.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/essentialrealestate-768x297.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>If you&#8217;re looking for a real estate plugin that allows frontend property listing submissions, then Essential Real Estate plugin is perfect. It has both backend and frontend support for listing submissions with a powerful dashboard for agents to manage their listings.</p>\n<p>It enables you to easily customize and set up a real estate website with all the features you need. Essential Real Estate plugin supports all global <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-stripe-payment-plugins-for-wordpress/\" title=\"6 Best Stripe Payment Plugins for WordPress (2018)\">payment methods</a> so you can build a real estate market online.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/birchpress/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"BirchPress\" rel=\"nofollow\">7. BirchPress</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/birchpress/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"BirchPress\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/birchpress.jpg\" alt=\"BirchPress\" width=\"775\" height=\"300\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-223548\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/birchpress.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/birchpress-300x116.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/birchpress-768x297.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>BirchPress is a WordPress <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/make-appointment-booking-system-wordpress/\" title=\"How to Make an Appointment Booking System with WordPress\">appointment booking and scheduling</a> plugin. It can be used as an addon on your real estate website to manage appointments between clients and agents.</p>\n<p>It allows you to easily <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-booking-plugins-compared/\" title=\"7 Best WordPress Booking Plugins Compared (2018)\">add a booking form</a> on your WordPress website and also integrates online payments through PayPal. It fully supports <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/woocommerce/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"WooCommerce\" rel=\"nofollow\">WooCommerce</a> and all its features, so you can easily sell properties online.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/wpcasa/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"WPCasa\" rel=\"nofollow\">8. WPCasa</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/wpcasa/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"WPCasa\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/wpcasa.jpg\" alt=\"WPCasa\" width=\"775\" height=\"300\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-223549\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/wpcasa.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/wpcasa-300x116.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/wpcasa-768x297.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>WPCasa is a real estate plugin for WordPress websites. It features multiple themes that can be used to create a fully flexible and powerful real estate platform for users. WPCasa has an easy-to-use interface and all the settings are simple to manage in WordPress.</p>\n<p>It supports an advanced search engine with multiple filters to quickly find property listings on your real estate website. You can use the WPCasa editor to add property information, location maps, image galleries, and more details about your listings easily.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/real-estate-listing-realtyna-wpl/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"WPL Real Estate\" rel=\"nofollow\">9. WPL Real Estate</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/real-estate-listing-realtyna-wpl/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"WPL Real Estate\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/wplrealestate.jpg\" alt=\"WPL real estate\" width=\"775\" height=\"299\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-223550\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/wplrealestate.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/wplrealestate-300x116.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/wplrealestate-768x296.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>WPL Real Estate is another free real estate solution for WordPress websites. It features a filterable search for users to find property listings. It offers a flexible frontend dashboard for users and agents to add their listing quickly. WPL Real Estate has the options for users to add their personal profile, property locations with Google maps, create stylish listings, custom fields, and more.</p>\n<p>It works great with all the most <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/must-have-wordpress-plugins-for-business-websites/\" title=\"25 Must Have WordPress Plugins for Business Websites (Expert Pick)\">popular WordPress plugins</a> and supports IDX listings in the premium version. You can reach out to the plugin&#8217;s developer to get custom features on request.</p>\n<p>We hope this article helped you find the best WordPress real estate plugins. You should also check out our hand-picked list of the <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-event-plugins/\" title=\"9 Best WordPress Events Plugins Compared (2018)\">best WordPress event plugins</a>.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-real-estate-plugins/\">9 Best WordPress Real Estate Plugins COMPARED (2018)</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com\">IsItWP - WordPress Technology Lookup Tool</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:63:\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-real-estate-plugins/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:7;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:57:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:56:\"9 Best WordPress Job Board Plugins and Themes (Compared)\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:63:\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-job-board-plugins-themes/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:71:\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-job-board-plugins-themes/#respond\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Wed, 31 Oct 2018 08:36:27 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:6:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:9:\"Resources\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"best wordpress job board themes\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:2;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:17:\"job board plugins\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:3;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:28:\"job board plugins and themes\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:4;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:16:\"job board themes\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:5;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:27:\"wordpress job board plugins\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:32:\"https://www.isitwp.com/?p=222561\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:589:\"<p>Do you want the best WordPress job board plugins and themes? Job board WordPress plugins and themes can be used to build a job portal or search engine for job listings easily. It helps you post new job openings and you can also allow other employers to add jobs on your blog. In this article, [&#8230;]</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-job-board-plugins-themes/\">9 Best WordPress Job Board Plugins and Themes (Compared)</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com\">IsItWP - WordPress Technology Lookup Tool</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:14:\"Editorial Team\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:16304:\"<p>Do you want the best WordPress job board plugins and themes? Job board WordPress plugins and themes can be used to build a job portal or search engine for job listings easily. It helps you post new job openings and you can also allow other employers to add jobs on your blog.</p>\n<p>In this article, we&#8217;ll share the best WordPress job board plugins and themes so you can spend less time searching for the right tools and more time putting them into action.</p>\n<h3>Creating a Job Board Using WordPress</h3>\n<p>WordPress is the best website builder in the world. Many of the <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/popular-big-name-brands-using-wordpress/\" title=\"46 Biggest Brands in the World Using WordPress Actively\">biggest brands use WordPress</a> for their websites. It&#8217;s super flexible and offers all of the amazing features you&#8217;ll need to build your own job board.</p>\n<p>You&#8217;ll find 2 kinds of WordPress websites: WordPress.com, which is a hosted platform; and WordPress.org, which is a self-hosted solution. You can view our side-by-side comparison on <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wordpress-com-vs-wordpress-org-one-really-better/\" title=\"WordPress.com vs. WordPress.org – Is One Really Better Than the Other?\">WordPress.com vs. WordPress.org</a> for more details.</p>\n<p>We recommend you use WordPress.org. It&#8217;s a complete solution with access to all the most incredible features you need to succeed.</p>\n<p>But, first, you&#8217;ll need a <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/difference-between-domain-name-and-web-hosting-revealed/\" title=\"What’s the Difference Between Domain Name and Web Hosting? (REVEALED)\">domain name and web hosting</a>.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/bluehost/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Bluehost\" rel=\"nofollow\">Bluehost</a> is our recommended hosting solution. It&#8217;s one of the top web hosting companies, and also WordPress core&#8217;s official hosting partner.</p>\n<p>For our users, they&#8217;re offering a free domain name, free SSL certificate, and a massive discount on web hosting.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/create-a-wordpress-account-on-bluehost.jpg\" alt=\"create a blog on bluehost\" width=\"775\" height=\"483\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-218254\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/create-a-wordpress-account-on-bluehost.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/create-a-wordpress-account-on-bluehost-300x187.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/create-a-wordpress-account-on-bluehost-768x479.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/bluehost/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"btn ltgreen light\">Click Here to Claim This Exclusive Bluehost Offer &raquo;</a></p>\n<p>Upon purchasing web hosting, you should follow our guide on <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/how-to-make-a-website-step-by-step/\" title=\"How to Make a Website in 2018- Step by Step (with Pictures)\">how to make a website</a> with WordPress.</p>\n<p>Now, let&#8217;s take a look at some of the best WordPress job board plugins and themes that you can install on your site.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/wp-job-hunter/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Job Hunter\" rel=\"nofollow\">1. WP Job Hunter</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/wp-job-hunter/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Job Hunter\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/wpjobhunter.jpg\" alt=\"WP Job Hunter\" width=\"775\" height=\"400\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-222574\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/wpjobhunter.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/wpjobhunter-300x155.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/wpjobhunter-768x396.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>WP Job Hunter is a WordPress job board plugin suitable to display jobs on your website or blog. You can also <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/legit-ways-to-make-money-online-blogging/\" title=\"30 Ways to Make Money Online Blogging (On the Side) in 2018\">make money online</a> by allowing paid job listings. It comes with a job portal widget that you can drag and drop in any of the widget-ready areas of your site to easily display jobs wherever you desire.</p>\n<p>It includes many custom and automated integrations that&#8217;ll make the setup process easy for you. It supports the most popular social media platforms, including Facebook, to add like and share features. WP Job Hunter also integrates with Google Maps to display the locations of the jobs to your users.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/jobsearch/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"JobSearch\" rel=\"nofollow\">2. JobSearch</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/jobsearch/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"JobSearch\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/jobsearch.jpg\" alt=\"JobSearch\" width=\"775\" height=\"400\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-222575\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/jobsearch.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/jobsearch-300x155.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/jobsearch-768x396.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>JobSearch is a premium WordPress job board plugin. It features job alerts, application tracking, a resume builder, social app logins, and more. It comes with an effective search tool that makes the job searching effortless for your users.</p>\n<p>It offers employers the ability to post complete details for each job, and candidates can shortlist the jobs of their choice. Your users can apply for jobs using social media platforms like Facebook and LinkedIn. It&#8217;s a translation-ready plugin and fully supports <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/woocommerce/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"WooCommerce\" rel=\"nofollow\">WooCommerce</a>.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/enginethemes-jobengine/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"JobEngine\" rel=\"nofollow\">3. JobEngine</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/enginethemes-jobengine/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"JobEngine\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/jobengine.jpg\" alt=\"JobEngine\" width=\"775\" height=\"400\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-222576\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/jobengine.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/jobengine-300x155.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/jobengine-768x396.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>JobEngine is a simple WordPress job board theme. It has all the features that you need to create a job portal. It&#8217;s highly customizable and flexible, allowing you to add new job listings easily. You can also allow employers to add their jobs on your website. For this, you can create multiple packages and charge them for each listing.</p>\n<p>It supports featured listing templates, payment gateways, multiple color schemes, custom theme options, sidebars, built-in landing pages, and more. It allows you to easily <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/easily-create-multilingual-wordpress-website/\" title=\"How to Easily Create a Multilingual WordPress Website (Step by Step)\">create a multilingual website</a>.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/appthemes-jobroller/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"JobRoller\" rel=\"nofollow\">4. JobRoller</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/appthemes-jobroller/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"JobRoller\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/jobroller.jpg\" alt=\"JobRoller\" width=\"775\" height=\"400\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-222577\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/jobroller.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/jobroller-300x155.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/jobroller-768x396.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>JobRoller is an excellent job board theme for WordPress websites. It ships with multiple sections for featured job listings, monetization options, landing pages, and an Ajax-based search filter.</p>\n<p>Furthermore, it&#8217;s easy to set up and includes custom theme options. JobRoller allows you and your users to create an account, upload job listings, manage a CV bank, and more. It&#8217;s a powerful WordPress theme for the job portals with simple, tidy layout.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/wp-job-manager/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"WP Job Manager\" rel=\"nofollow\">5. WP Job Manager</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/wp-job-manager/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"WP Job Manager\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/wpjobmanager.jpg\" alt=\"WP Job Manager\" width=\"775\" height=\"360\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-222578\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/wpjobmanager.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/wpjobmanager-300x139.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/wpjobmanager-768x357.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>WP Job Manager is a flexible WordPress job board plugin with amazing features. It allows you to easily create a job board with needed pages, <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/custom-user-registration-form-wordpress/\" title=\"How to Create a Custom User Registration Form in WordPress\">user registration</a> form, and job listings. It offers a custom dashboard for your users to upload new jobs, manage listings, and more.</p>\n<p>It comes with multiple addons. It integrates your job board with Facebook, <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/woocommerce/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"WooCommerce\" rel=\"nofollow\">WooCommerce</a>, Indeed, and other useful apps.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/job-board-manager/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Job Board Manager\" rel=\"nofollow\">6. Job Board Manager</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/job-board-manager/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Job Board Manager\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/jobboardmanager.jpg\" alt=\"Job Board Manager\" width=\"775\" height=\"380\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-222579\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/jobboardmanager.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/jobboardmanager-300x147.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/jobboardmanager-768x377.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Job Board Manager is a free WordPress job board plugin that can be used to launch your job portal quickly. It features company profiles, Geo locations, custom widgets, and premium addons. It allows you to add the job listings on multiple pages and posts using shortcodes.</p>\n<p>Moreover, you can add new job listings, create paid listing sections, manage job alerts, and more. It supports Schema.org rich snippets, a job application dashboard, WooCommerce stores, and breadcrumbs.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/apply-online/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Apply Online\" rel=\"nofollow\">7. Apply Online</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/apply-online/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Apply Online\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/applyonline.jpg\" alt=\"Apply Online\" width=\"775\" height=\"385\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-222580\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/applyonline.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/applyonline-300x149.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/applyonline-768x382.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>As the name suggests, Apply Online is a WordPress job board plugin that lets users apply for jobs online. It&#8217;s suitable for classified ads management, accepts job applications, allows users to apply for jobs online, and sends email alerts.</p>\n<p>It comes with search filters, job listing categories, online <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/create-job-application-form-wordpress/\" title=\"How to Create a Job Application Form in WordPress (Step by Step)\">job application forms</a>, and custom job ads. There&#8217;s no facility to add paid listings, so you&#8217;ll need to use a companion plugin that offers paid subscriptions. You can also <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/add-contact-form-wordpress-website/\" title=\"How to Add a Contact Form to Your WordPress Website\">create a contact form</a> to receive applications from employers for custom listings.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/simple-job-board/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Simple Job Board\" rel=\"nofollow\">8. Simple Job Board</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/simple-job-board/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Simple Job Board\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/simplejobboard.jpg\" alt=\"Simple Job Board\" width=\"775\" height=\"385\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-222581\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/simplejobboard.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/simplejobboard-300x149.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/simplejobboard-768x382.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>If you&#8217;re looking for a simple, easy solution to add a job portal onto your WordPress site, then try Simple Job Board plugin. It gives you a full control of your job listings. The plugin&#8217;s not bloated with features. You&#8217;ll need to manually create job listings, add categories, and more. It doesn&#8217;t allow your users to create an account or add paid listings, so you&#8217;ll need to create a form on your website to accept offers from employers.</p>\n<p>With all the limitations comes flexibility as it gives you access to add complete details for job listings, show custom application forms to candidates, and more.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wpjobboard.net/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"WPJobBoard\" rel=\"nofollow\">9. WPJobBoard</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wpjobboard.net/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"WPJobBoard\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/wpjobboard.jpg\" alt=\"WP Job Board\" width=\"775\" height=\"400\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-222582\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/wpjobboard.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/wpjobboard-300x155.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/wpjobboard-768x396.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>WPJobBoard is a powerful WordPress plugin to create a job board on your blog. It comes with a custom portal for employers to look at the new applications and select the best candidates. It has a front-end panel that allows users to <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/create-file-upload-form-wordpress-step-step/\" title=\"How to Create a File Upload Form in WordPress – (Step by Step)\">upload files</a> like CVs, add new job listings, and more.</p>\n<p>It&#8217;s bundled with a free job board theme that can be used to easily create a job portal website. It&#8217;s also fully flexible with the <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-responsive-wordpress-themes/\" title=\"50+ Best Responsive WordPress Themes\">best WordPress themes</a>. It supports payment gateways, memberships, discounts, coupons, and <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/coupons/\" title=\"Top Coupons &#038; Deals From Our Favorite Stores\">deals</a>.</p>\n<p>We hope this article helped you find the best WordPress job board plugins and themes. You may also want to see our expert pick of the <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-vpn-services-wordpress-users-compared/\" title=\"7 Best VPN Services for WordPress Users COMPARED (2018)\">best VPN services for WordPress users</a>.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-job-board-plugins-themes/\">9 Best WordPress Job Board Plugins and Themes (Compared)</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com\">IsItWP - WordPress Technology Lookup Tool</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:68:\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-job-board-plugins-themes/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:8;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:57:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:57:\"19 Best WordPress Plugins for Non-profits &amp; Charities\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:57:\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-plugins-nonprofits/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:65:\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-plugins-nonprofits/#respond\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Tue, 30 Oct 2018 06:52:01 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:6:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:17:\"WordPress Plugins\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:37:\"best wordpress plugins for nonprofits\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:2;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:22:\"plugins for nonprofits\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:3;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:44:\"plugins for nonprofits to support your cause\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:4;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:17:\"wordpress plugins\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:5;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:32:\"wordpress plugins for nonprofits\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:32:\"https://www.isitwp.com/?p=222689\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:618:\"<p>Do you want the best WordPress plugins for nonprofits to add features on your site? Nonprofits need WordPress plugins that can support their cause and help them build a website on a tight budget. The perfect plugins allow nonprofits to launch their website without hiring any developer, so they can save money for what really [&#8230;]</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-plugins-nonprofits/\">19 Best WordPress Plugins for Non-profits &#038; Charities</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com\">IsItWP - WordPress Technology Lookup Tool</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:14:\"Editorial Team\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:27769:\"<p>Do you want the best WordPress plugins for nonprofits to add features on your site? Nonprofits need WordPress plugins that can support their cause and help them build a website on a tight budget. The perfect plugins allow nonprofits to launch their website without hiring any developer, so they can save money for what really matters: their cause.</p>\n<p>In this article, we&#8217;ll share the best WordPress plugins for nonprofits to support your cause.</p>\n<h3>Making a Nonprofits Website with WordPress</h3>\n<p>WordPress is the most popular website builder in the world. You&#8217;ve likely noticed many of the <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/popular-big-name-brands-using-wordpress/\" title=\"46 Biggest Brands in the World Using WordPress Actively\">biggest brands in the world using WordPress actively</a> on their sites.</p>\n<p>When starting, you&#8217;ll encounter 2 types of WordPress sites: WordPress.com, which is a hosted platform; and WordPress.org, which is a self-hosted solution. See our detailed comparison between <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wordpress-com-vs-wordpress-org-one-really-better/\" title=\"WordPress.com vs. WordPress.org – Is One Really Better Than the Other?\">WordPress.com vs WordPress.org</a> for more information.</p>\n<p>For your site, we recommend using self-hosted WordPress.org as it has all the features and options you&#8217;ll need. If you&#8217;re already using WordPress.com, then you can <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/how-to-move-your-site-from-wordpress-com-to-wordpress-org/\" title=\"How to Move Your Site From WordPress.com to WordPress.org\">move your site from WordPress.com to WordPress.org</a>.</p>\n<p>But, first, you&#8217;ll need a <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/difference-between-domain-name-and-web-hosting-revealed/\" title=\"What’s the Difference Between Domain Name and Web Hosting? (REVEALED)\">domain name and web hosting</a>.</p>\n<p>We recommend <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/bluehost/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Bluehost\" rel=\"nofollow\">Bluehost</a>. It&#8217;s officially recommended by WordPress core, and 1 of the popular web hosting companies in the world.</p>\n<p>Luckily, they&#8217;re offering our users a free domain name, free SSL certificate, and a massive discount on web hosting.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/create-a-wordpress-account-on-bluehost.jpg\" alt=\"create a blog on bluehost\" width=\"775\" height=\"483\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-218254\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/create-a-wordpress-account-on-bluehost.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/create-a-wordpress-account-on-bluehost-300x187.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/create-a-wordpress-account-on-bluehost-768x479.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/bluehost/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"btn ltgreen light\">Click Here to Claim This Exclusive Bluehost Offer &raquo;</a></p>\n<p>Once purchased, you can follow our step-by-step guide on <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/how-to-make-a-website-step-by-step/\" title=\"How to Make a Website in 2018- Step by Step (with Pictures)\">how to make a website</a>.</p>\n<p>Now, let&#8217;s take a look at the best WordPress plugins for nonprofits you can use on your WordPress site.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wpforms.com/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"WPForms\">1. WPForms</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wpforms.com/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"WPForms\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/wpforms.jpg\" alt=\"WPForms\" width=\"775\" height=\"400\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-222076\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/wpforms.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/wpforms-300x155.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/wpforms-768x396.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>WPForms is the <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-contact-form-plugins/\" title=\"7 Best WordPress Contact Form Plugins Compared (2018)\">best WordPress contact form plugin</a>. It&#8217;s super flexible and comes with great features to add a contact form, <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/create-wordpress-donation-form/\" title=\"How to Create a WordPress Donation Form (Step by Step)\">donation form</a>, and other useful forms on your WordPress site.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/wpforms-lite/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"WPForms Lite\" rel=\"nofollow\">WPForms Lite</a> is the free version of the plugin. It can be used by <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/create-small-business-website-simple-steps/\" title=\"How to Create a Small Business Website in 5 Simple Steps (2018)\">small business websites</a>, nonprofits, and blogs to add a simple contact form easily. Their paid version comes with more features and options like payment addons. </p>\n<p>WPForms integrates with all the <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-email-marketing-services-compared/\" title=\"9 Best Email Marketing Services Compared (2018)\">best email marketing services</a> like <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/aweber/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"AWeber\" rel=\"nofollow\">AWeber</a>, <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/mailchimp/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"MailChimp\" rel=\"nofollow\">MailChimp</a>, <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/constant-contact/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Constant Contact\" rel=\"nofollow\">Constant Contact</a>, and more.</p>\n<p>It also works great with payment services like PayPal and Stripe to collect online donations.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"MonsterInsights\">2. MonsterInsights</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"MonsterInsights\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/monsterinsights.jpg\" alt=\"MonsterInsights\" width=\"775\" height=\"400\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-222077\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/monsterinsights.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/monsterinsights-300x155.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/monsterinsights-768x396.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>MonsterInsights is the <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-analytics-solutions-compared/\" title=\"7 Best WordPress Analytics Solutions Compared (2018)\">best WordPress analytics solution</a> on the market. It shows your website traffic stats in your WordPress dashboard. MonsterInsights has many powerful addons to customize the Google Analytics reports for your site.</p>\n<p>They offer multiple pricing plans for small-to-big websites which means you can easily use MonsterInsights on your nonprofit website to add Google Analytics in WordPress.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/givewp/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"GiveWP\" rel=\"nofollow\">3. GiveWP</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/givewp/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"GiveWP\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/givewp.jpg\" alt=\"GiveWP\" width=\"775\" height=\"400\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-222707\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/givewp.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/givewp-300x155.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/givewp-768x396.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>GiveWP is an excellent WordPress nonprofits plugin. It comes with all the features you&#8217;ll need to accept online donations, manage the money given, and more within your WordPress dashboard. You can easily create a donation form and integrate a payment gateway to collect donations from users.</p>\n<p>Speaking of payment gateways, GiveWP can be easily connected with the most popular payment services, like PayPal. On top of that, you can also connect your donation form with the popular email services, including AWeber and MailChimp.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"OptinMonster\">4. OptinMonster</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"OptinMonster\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/optinmonster.jpg\" alt=\"OptinMonster\" width=\"775\" height=\"400\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-222709\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/optinmonster.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/optinmonster-300x155.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/optinmonster-768x396.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>OptinMonster is the <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-lead-generation-plugins-compared/\" title=\"7 Best WordPress Lead Generation Plugins Compared (2018)\">best WordPress lead generation plugin</a> in the world. You can use this plugin on your nonprofit site to make sure visitors donate to your cause before leaving your site.</p>\n<p>It offers multiple optin popup styles including slide in, sidebar, lightbox, and more. OptinMonster has helped many businesses and nonprofits to grow their subscribers exponentially.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/easy-digital-downloads/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Easy Digital Downloads\" rel=\"nofollow\">5. Easy Digital Downloads</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/easy-digital-downloads/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Easy Digital Downloads\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/easydigitaldownloads.jpg\" alt=\"Easy Digital Downloads\" width=\"775\" height=\"400\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-222708\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/easydigitaldownloads.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/easydigitaldownloads-300x155.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/easydigitaldownloads-768x396.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Easy Digital Downloads is one of the most popular <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-ecommerce-plugins-compared/\" title=\"7 Best WordPress eCommerce Plugins Compared (2018)\">WordPress eCommerce plugins</a>. It allows you to sell digital downloads, like eBooks, to collect money for your nonprofit cause. </p>\n<p>Easy Digital Downloads has powerful addons to integrate payment gateways, services, and more.</p>\n<p>It works great on all the <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/top-wordpress-themes/\" title=\"The Best and Most Popular WordPress Themes of 2018 (UPDATED)\">best WordPress themes</a>. It&#8217;s flexible and easy to set up on your site.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/wp-super-cache/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"WP Super Cache\" rel=\"nofollow\">6. WP Super Cache</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/wp-super-cache/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"WP Super Cache\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/wpsupercache.jpg\" alt=\"WP Super Cache\" width=\"775\" height=\"400\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-222725\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/wpsupercache.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/wpsupercache-300x155.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/wpsupercache-768x396.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>WP Super Cache is a popular <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-caching-plugins-compared/\" title=\"7 Best WordPress Caching Plugins Compared (2018)\">caching plugin for WordPress</a> sites. It&#8217;s free to download and use. It comes with amazing caching features that&#8217;ll help you improve the performance of your nonprofit website.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wordpress-plugins/wp-super-cache/\" title=\"WP Super Cache Review 2018: Is It the Best WordPress Caching Plugin?\">WP Super Cache</a> offers page cache, CDN support, cache pre-loading, gzip compression, and more. It&#8217;s easy to set up and all settings are beginner-friendly.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/sucuri/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Sucuri Scanner\" rel=\"nofollow\">7. Sucuri</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/sucuri/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Sucuri Scanner\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/sucuri.jpg\" alt=\"Sucuri\" width=\"775\" height=\"400\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-222080\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/sucuri.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/sucuri-300x155.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/sucuri-768x396.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Sucuri is the top <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-security-plugins-compared/\" title=\"6 Best WordPress Security Plugins Compared (2018)\">WordPress security plugin</a>. It creates a secure wall between your users and your website to protect you from unwanted visitors. <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wordpress-plugins/sucuri/\" title=\"Sucuri Review 2018: Why We Love Sucuri + Pros and Cons\">Sucuri</a> has amazing features that&#8217;ll keep your website secure from malware and hackers.</p>\n<p>It&#8217;s a recommended plugin for nonprofit sites who accept online donations to maintain security for your donors.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/updraftplus/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"UpdraftPlus\" rel=\"nofollow\">8. UpdraftPlus</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/updraftplus/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"UpdraftPlus\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/updraftplus.jpg\" alt=\"UpdraftPlus\" width=\"775\" height=\"400\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-222079\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/updraftplus.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/updraftplus-300x155.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/updraftplus-768x396.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>UpdraftPlus is a popular <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-backup-plugins-compared/\" title=\"9 Best WordPress Backup Plugins Compared (2018)\">backup plugin for WordPress</a> sites. It allows you to easily <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/easily-backup-wordpress-site-step-step/\" title=\"How to Easily Back Up Your WordPress Site (Step by Step)\">back up your WordPress site</a>.</p>\n<p>Once you&#8217;ve created your nonprofit site, you&#8217;ll want to make sure it&#8217;s up and running, always. <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wordpress-plugins/updraftplus-review/\" title=\"UpdraftPlus Review: Is It the Best WordPress Backup Plugin?\">UpdraftPlus</a> helps you maintain regular backups of your site. It also allows you to easily restore your site from the backups anytime you need to.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/wordpress-seo/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Yoast SEO\" rel=\"nofollow\">9. Yoast SEO</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/wordpress-seo/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Yoast SEO\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/yoastseo.jpg\" alt=\"Yoast SEO\" width=\"775\" height=\"400\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-222083\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/yoastseo.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/yoastseo-300x155.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/yoastseo-768x396.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Yoast SEO is the most popular WordPress SEO plugin on the market. It helps you optimize your website for search engines, so you&#8217;ll attract the best visitors who actually want to support your cause. <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wordpress-plugins/yoast-seo/\" title=\"Yoast SEO Review 2018: Is It the Best WordPress SEO Plugin?\">Yoast SEO</a> has many features that can be used to improve your search engine rankings.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/envira-gallery/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Envira Gallery\" rel=\"nofollow\">10. Envira Gallery</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/envira-gallery/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Envira Gallery\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/enviragallery.jpg\" alt=\"Envira Gallery\" width=\"775\" height=\"400\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-222078\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/enviragallery.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/enviragallery-300x155.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/enviragallery-768x396.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Envira Gallery is one of the top <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-gallery-plugins-compared/\" title=\"7 Best WordPress Gallery Plugins Compared (2018)\">WordPress image gallery plugins</a>. Many nonprofits want to show their images to new visitors to convince them to donate, which is why <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wordpress-plugins/envira-gallery/\" title=\"Envira Gallery Review 2018 – The Best WordPress Gallery Plugin\">Envira Gallery</a> is an important plugin for the nonprofit sites.</p>\n<p>It allows you to present your photos in beautiful, professional image galleries. It has amazing features like lightbox popup, masonry galleries, polaroid effects, and more.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/testimonials-widget/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Testimonials Widget\" rel=\"nofollow\">11. Testimonials Widget</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/testimonials-widget/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Testimonials Widget\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/testimonialwidgets.jpg\" alt=\"Testimonials Widget\" width=\"775\" height=\"400\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-222727\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/testimonialwidgets.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/testimonialwidgets-300x155.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/testimonialwidgets-768x396.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Testimonials Widget is a free WordPress testimonials plugin. It&#8217;s important for nonprofit sites to display testimonials from their donors. The plugin is beginner-friendly and easy to set up.</p>\n<p>It allows you to show testimonials anywhere, including posts, pages, and widget-ready areas. You can add the testimonials widget in your sidebar, footer, or any other widget-supported sections in WordPress.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/quick-and-easy-faqs/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Quick and Easy FAQs\" rel=\"nofollow\">12. Quick and Easy FAQs</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/quick-and-easy-faqs/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Quick and Easy FAQs\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/quickeasyfaqs.jpg\" alt=\"Quick and Easy FAQs\" width=\"785\" height=\"405\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-222728\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/quickeasyfaqs.jpg 785w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/quickeasyfaqs-300x155.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/quickeasyfaqs-768x396.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 785px) 100vw, 785px\" /></a></p>\n<p>As the name suggests, Quick and Easy FAQs is an easy-to-use WordPress FAQs plugin. You can use this plugin to add frequently asked questions, with answers, onto your nonprofit site. It saves the time for you and your visitors. The plugin has many templates to present FAQs beautifully.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/tablepress/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"TablePress\" rel=\"nofollow\">13. TablePress</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/tablepress/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"TablePress\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/tablepress.jpg\" alt=\"TablePress\" width=\"775\" height=\"356\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-222729\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/tablepress.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/tablepress-300x138.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/tablepress-768x353.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>TablePress is a free WordPress plugin to add tables, using a simple drag and drop interface, on your site. You can use these tables on your nonprofit site to display donation charts and other stats to your visitors.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/google-calendar-events/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Simple Calendar – Google Calendar Plugin\" rel=\"nofollow\">14. Simple Calendar</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/google-calendar-events/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Simple Calendar – Google Calendar Plugin\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/simplecalendar.jpg\" alt=\"Simple Calendar\" width=\"775\" height=\"400\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-222730\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/simplecalendar.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/simplecalendar-300x155.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/simplecalendar-768x396.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Simple Calendar is a Google Calendar plugin that lets you to create events and display them on your nonprofit site. It allows your visitors to subscribe to the calendar, and they&#8217;ll get notifications for new events.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/forget-about-shortcode-buttons/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Forget About Shortcode Buttons\" rel=\"nofollow\">15. Forget About Shortcode Buttons</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/forget-about-shortcode-buttons/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Forget About Shortcode Buttons\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/forgetaboutshortcodebuttons.jpg\" alt=\"Forget About Shortcode Buttons\" width=\"775\" height=\"396\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-222739\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/forgetaboutshortcodebuttons.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/forgetaboutshortcodebuttons-300x153.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/forgetaboutshortcodebuttons-768x392.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Forget About Shortcode Buttons is a free WordPress plugin to add stunning buttons onto your nonprofit site. You need to add multiple call-to-action buttons on different pages and posts to make people visit your <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-landing-page-plugins/\" title=\"7 Best WordPress Landing Page Plugins That Convert (2018)\">landing pages</a> or donation forms. This unique plugin will help you easily add buttons without the help of shortcodes.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/polylang/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Polylang\" rel=\"nofollow\">16. Polylang</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/polylang/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Polylang\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/polylang.jpg\" alt=\"Polylang\" width=\"775\" height=\"400\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-222744\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/polylang.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/polylang-300x155.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/polylang-768x396.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Polylang is a WordPress plugin that offers bilingual and multilingual support. It allows you to <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/easily-create-multilingual-wordpress-website/\" title=\"How to Easily Create a Multilingual WordPress Website (Step by Step)\">create a multilingual nonprofit site</a>, so anyone in the world can read and follow your content in their own language. It allows your visitors to easily switch the website&#8217;s language into their own language.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/floating-social-bar/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Floating Social bar\" rel=\"nofollow\">17. Floating Social bar</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/floating-social-bar/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Floating Social bar\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/floatingsocialbar.jpg\" alt=\"Floating Social Bar\" width=\"775\" height=\"400\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-222748\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/floatingsocialbar.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/floatingsocialbar-300x155.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/floatingsocialbar-768x396.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>If you want to add social sharing buttons onto your WordPress site in a beautiful and modern style, then you&#8217;ll need the <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wordpress-plugins/floating-social-bar/\" title=\"Floating Social Bar\">Floating Social Bar</a> plugin. It&#8217;s a free <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-social-media-plugins/\" title=\"12 Best WordPress Social Media Plugins (2018)\">social sharing plugin</a> for nonprofit sites to easily share their cause on social media platforms. Your visitors can share the pages and posts on social media channels quickly with just 1 click.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/tweet-old-post/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Revive Old Post\" rel=\"nofollow\">18. Revive Old Post</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/tweet-old-post/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Revive Post\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/revivepost.jpg\" alt=\"Revive Post\" width=\"775\" height=\"400\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-222749\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/revivepost.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/revivepost-300x155.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/revivepost-768x396.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Revive Old Post is another interesting WordPress plugin that automatically shares your old posts on social media. It saves you time via its automation process. You should use this plugin on your nonprofit site to promote your old posts and keep your social sites engaged.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/mappress-google-maps-for-wordpress/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"MapPress Maps\" rel=\"nofollow\">19. MapPress Google Maps</a></h3>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/mappress.jpg\" alt=\"MapPress Google Maps\" width=\"775\" height=\"400\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-222750\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/mappress.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/mappress-300x155.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/mappress-768x396.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></p>\n<p>MapPress Google Maps is a WordPress plugin for sharing the location of your nonprofit centre. It features easy-to-embed maps that you can place on your WordPress pages and posts. It allows you to mark destinations, add directions, and more.</p>\n<p>We hope this article helped you find best WordPress plugins for nonprofits. You should also check out our hand-picked <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-responsive-wordpress-themes/\" title=\"50+ Best Responsive WordPress Themes\">best responsive WordPress themes</a>.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-plugins-nonprofits/\">19 Best WordPress Plugins for Non-profits &#038; Charities</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com\">IsItWP - WordPress Technology Lookup Tool</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:62:\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-plugins-nonprofits/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:9;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:57:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:56:\"How to Properly Add Code Snippets to Your WordPress Site\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:65:\"https://www.isitwp.com/properly-add-code-snippets-wordpress-site/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:73:\"https://www.isitwp.com/properly-add-code-snippets-wordpress-site/#respond\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Mon, 29 Oct 2018 19:35:44 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:6:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:19:\"WordPress Tutorials\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:13:\"code snippets\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:2;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:13:\"functions.php\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:3;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:20:\"site specific plugin\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:4;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:14:\"template files\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:5;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:19:\"wordpress templates\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:32:\"https://www.isitwp.com/?p=223876\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:625:\"<p>Want to know the proper way to add custom code snippets to your WordPress site? Adding code snippets to WordPress isn’t rocket science, but even the slightest mistake could crash your website. If you jump in without knowing what you&#8217;re doing, it could be fatal to your business. So, when you’re adding custom code to [&#8230;]</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/properly-add-code-snippets-wordpress-site/\">How to Properly Add Code Snippets to Your WordPress Site</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com\">IsItWP - WordPress Technology Lookup Tool</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:14:\"Editorial Team\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:8991:\"<p>Want to know the proper way to add custom code snippets to your WordPress site? Adding code snippets to WordPress isn’t rocket science, but even the slightest mistake could crash your website. If you jump in without knowing what you&#8217;re doing, it could be fatal to your business.</p>\n<p>So, when you’re adding custom code to your site, you’ll need to make sure you’re doing it the RIGHT WAY.</p>\n<p>In this article, we’ll explain how to properly copy and paste code snippets to your WordPress site. Once you&#8217;ve finished reading, you&#8217;ll have the knowledge and the confidence to modify your site as you please. You might even have a bit of FUN!</p>\n<h3>Why Add Code Snippets to WordPress?</h3>\n<p>Adding code snippets to your site is one of the easiest ways to extend your website’s features. Although installing a plugin is the obvious way to enhance the built-in features of WordPress, especially for non-developers, at times, it’s hard to find a plugin that addresses your needs to the letter. On the other hand, you can find hundreds of WordPress tutorials on the web that recommend adding code snippets to meet your needs.</p>\n<p>That said, it’s essential for you to properly insert the custom code snippets in the correct file and in the right location. Otherwise, it could crash your website, in turn sabotaging your business and reputation.</p>\n<p>Let’s break down this tutorial into 2 different sections:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>Customizing WordPress template files</li>\n<li>Customizing functions.php file</li>\n</ol>\n<h3>I. Customizing WordPress Template Files</h3>\n<p>Before we dive in, let’s take a look at what a WordPress template file is.</p>\n<p><strong>What&#8217;s a WordPress Template?</strong></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/customize-a-template.png\" alt=\"customize a template\" width=\"740\" height=\"379\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-223878\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/customize-a-template.png 740w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/customize-a-template-300x154.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 740px) 100vw, 740px\" /></p>\n<p>Every WordPress theme is made up of template files. The template files on your theme define how your website is displayed. For example, header.php is a default template used in most WordPress themes to define the header area of your WordPress-generated web pages, such as your blog articles and standalone pages.</p>\n<p>Let’s take a look at a few default WordPress templates used by most WordPress themes.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>php – defines the main page</li>\n<li>php – defines the header section</li>\n<li>php – defines the footer section</li>\n<li>php – defines the functions used in the theme</li>\n<li>php – defines the single post / blog post</li>\n<li>php – defines the standalone page</li>\n<li>php – defines the comments section</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>How to Insert Snippets Into Any Template File</h3>\n<p>You can insert code snippets into any template file, such as functions.php, single.php, etc. by either of these 2 methods: by using a child theme or by adding the code directly to your existing parent theme.</p>\n<p>However, it’s advised not to customize the template directly in your parent theme because, when you upgrade your theme, you’ll lose all the customizations you’ve made. To preserve the tweaks even after upgrading your theme, you might want to create a child theme and make customization within it.</p>\n<p>A child theme is a WordPress theme that inherits its functionality from another WordPress theme (the parent theme). Using a child theme is the right choice if you want to make a lot of tweaks to your template files.</p>\n<p>Let’s take a look at how to create a child theme and insert snippets into your template file.</p>\n<p>For a detailed guide, you can check out <a href=\"https://www.wpbeginner.com/wp-themes/how-to-create-a-wordpress-child-theme-video/\">how to create a child theme on WordPress</a>.</p>\n<h3>II. Customizing functions.php file</h3>\n<p><strong>What&#8217;s functions.php file?</strong></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/functions.php-file.png\" alt=\"functions.php file\" width=\"740\" height=\"397\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-223879\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/functions.php-file.png 740w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/functions.php-file-300x161.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 740px) 100vw, 740px\" /></p>\n<p>functions.php is a template file in your WordPress theme that enables you to easily extend the features of your theme and WordPress installation. To extend the features, all you have to do is add certain code snippets to your functions.php file.</p>\n<p>Just like any other template files, you can add snippets directly to your functions.php file. In addition, to retain the customization even after upgrading your theme, you can create a child theme and insert the code within it.</p>\n<p>However, the downside is that you’ll lose all the customization you’ve made on a child theme if you switch over to a new/different theme. This is where a site-specific plugin comes in.</p>\n<p>A site-specific WordPress plugin is independent of your theme, which allows you to add custom snippets to your site. You can use site-specific plugin in 2 ways:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Method #1: Using a ready-made plugin, such as Code Snippets</li>\n<li>Method #2: Manually creating a site-specific plugin</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Method #1: Using a Readymade Plugin</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/code-snippets/\">Code Snippets</a> is a <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/top-wordpress-plugins/\">WordPress plugin</a> that provides a graphical interface for managing snippets similar to the Plugins menu.</p>\n<p>It removes the need to insert custom snippets to your theme’s functions.php file. Since you’re not inserting the code in any theme files, you can preserve the customization on your site even after switching your theme.</p>\n<p>With Code Snippets, you can activate or deactivate snippets, just like plugins.</p>\n<p>Once you’ve activated <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/code-snippets/\">the Code Snippets plugin</a>, you can add custom snippets, and then specify a title, description, and tags for the snippets as reference for yourself down the line. That way, in the future, you can easily figure out the purpose of each snippet you&#8217;ve added.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/add-custom-snippet-with-custom-snippets-plugin2.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"727\" height=\"415\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-223697\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/add-custom-snippet-with-custom-snippets-plugin2.png 727w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/add-custom-snippet-with-custom-snippets-plugin2-300x171.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 727px) 100vw, 727px\" /></p>\n<p>For more details, you can read our post on <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/create-wordpress-site-specific-plugin-easy-guide/\">how to create a site-specific plugin</a>.</p>\n<h3>2. Create a Site-Specific Plan and Insert the Code</h3>\n<p>You can manually create a site-specific plugin and insert the code within it. Unlike a ready-made plugin, a manually-created site-specific plugin is usually a basic, lightweight plugin that doesn’t have a graphical interface for managing snippets.</p>\n<p>To make customizations, you can head over to the plugin editor and insert the code into it.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/add-your-snippets-to-site-specific-plugin.png\" alt=\"add your snippets to site-specific plugin\" width=\"748\" height=\"378\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-223677\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/add-your-snippets-to-site-specific-plugin.png 748w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/add-your-snippets-to-site-specific-plugin-300x152.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 748px) 100vw, 748px\" /></p>\n<p>For a step-by-step guide, you can check out <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/create-wordpress-site-specific-plugin-easy-guide/\">creating a site-specific plugin</a>.</p>\n<p>That’s it!</p>\n<p>We hope this guide helped you add code snippets to your <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/how-to-make-a-website-step-by-step/\">WordPress site</a>.</p>\n<p>Now, go ahead and <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/snippets/\">find some code snippets</a> that you can add to enhance your WordPress&#8217; functionalities.</p>\n<p>If you liked this article, you may also want to check out <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/must-have-wordpress-plugins-for-business-websites/\">must-have plugins for business website</a>.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/properly-add-code-snippets-wordpress-site/\">How to Properly Add Code Snippets to Your WordPress Site</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com\">IsItWP - WordPress Technology Lookup Tool</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:70:\"https://www.isitwp.com/properly-add-code-snippets-wordpress-site/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}}}s:27:\"http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom\";a:1:{s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:3:{s:4:\"href\";s:28:\"https://www.isitwp.com/feed/\";s:3:\"rel\";s:4:\"self\";s:4:\"type\";s:19:\"application/rss+xml\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:44:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/syndication/\";a:2:{s:12:\"updatePeriod\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:6:\"hourly\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:15:\"updateFrequency\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"1\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}}}}}}}}s:4:\"type\";i:128;s:7:\"headers\";O:42:\"Requests_Utility_CaseInsensitiveDictionary\":1:{s:7:\"\0*\0data\";a:18:{s:6:\"ser